msgctxt "4140_Kiryu"
msgid "Have you been working here long?"
msgstr "¿Llevas mucho tiempo trabajando?"

msgctxt "4152_Maya"
msgid "Compared to the other girls, I guess so."
msgstr "A comparación con las otras chicas, creo que sí."

msgctxt "4164_Kiryu"
msgid "I see."
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "4176_Maya"
msgid "But I've been thinking about quitting recently."
msgstr "Pero, últimamente, estaba pensando en renunciar."

msgctxt "4188_Kiryu"
msgid "Really? Why?"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¿Por qué?"

msgctxt "4200_Maya"
msgid "Hahaha! That's not something that I'd share with a first time customer."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! No es algo que compartiría con un cliente nuevo. "

msgctxt "4212_Kiryu"
msgid "Is there a reason why you have to quit?"
msgstr "¿Pero hay una razón por la que tienes que renunciar?"

msgctxt "4224_Maya"
msgid "Well... I also work as a model."
msgstr "Bueno... También trabajo como modelo."

msgctxt "4236_Kiryu"
msgid "Ah. I should've known. You're so pretty, after all."
msgstr "Ah. Debería de haberlo sabido. Después de todo, eres preciosa."

msgctxt "4248_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. Thank you. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Je, je. Gracias. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4260_Maya"
msgid "I originally started here because my boyfriend worked at night, and I wanted to be on the same schedule."
msgstr "Comencé aquí debido a que mi novio trabajaba en la noche, y yo quería estar en el mismo horario."

msgctxt "4272_Maya"
msgid "But I broke up with him a while ago, and I've been busy with modeling work, so I'm thinking about quitting my job here."
msgstr "Pero rompí con el hace tiempo, y ahí estuve ocupada con el trabajo de modelaje, así que estoy pensando en dejar este trabajo."

msgctxt "4284_Kiryu"
msgid "That's too bad. When do you plan on quitting?"
msgstr "Que lastima. ¿Hasta cuando piensas renunciar?"

msgctxt "4296_Maya"
msgid "The sooner the better, I guess."
msgstr "Cuanto antes, mejor."

msgctxt "4308_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "Oh."

msgctxt "4320_Maya"
msgid "Aw. Are you disappointed you won't be able to see me?"
msgstr "Oh. ¿Te entristece no poder verme?"

msgctxt "4332_Kiryu"
msgid "A little. I don't know you very well yet."
msgstr "Un poco. Aunque no te conozca del todo."

msgctxt "4344_Maya"
msgid "That's true. We just met."
msgstr "Eso es cierto. Apenas nos conocemos."

msgctxt "4356_Maya"
msgid "But I wouldn't mind getting to know you better. Maybe I can stay a bit longer."
msgstr "Pero no me molestaría conocerte un poco más. Quizás me pueda quedar un poco más."

msgctxt "4368_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. All right, then. I'll come back and see you."
msgstr "Je, está bien. Entonces volveré a verte."

msgctxt "4380_Kiryu"
msgid "You did that for your boyfriend? Wow. I don't think most girls would do that."
msgstr "¿Dices que lo hiciste por tu novio? Vaya. Dudo mucho que la mayoría de chicas harían algo similar."

msgctxt "4392_Maya"
msgid "Well, I was thinking about his career, too. I couldn't have him changing jobs all the time."
msgstr "Bueno, yo también estaba pensando en su carrera. No podía tenerlo cambiando de trabajo todo el tiempo."

msgctxt "4404_Maya"
msgid "It was easier for me to work around his schedule."
msgstr "Era más fácil para mí trabajar con su horario."

msgctxt "4416_Kiryu"
msgid "Still, that was good of you."
msgstr "Pese a eso, eso fue bueno de tu parte."

msgctxt "4428_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. Thanks. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Je, je. Gracias. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4440_Maya"
msgid "But we broke up, so it doesn't matter now."
msgstr "Pero rompimos, así que ya no importa."

msgctxt "4452_Kiryu"
msgid "Why don't you stay for a bit longer?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no te quedas un poco más?"

msgctxt "4464_Maya"
msgid "Huh? Why?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Por qué?"

msgctxt "4476_Kiryu"
msgid "We just met. I'd like to get to know you better."
msgstr "Acabamos de conocernos. Y me gustaría conocerte un poco mejor."

msgctxt "4488_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. You're cute."
msgstr "Je, je. Eres lindo."

msgctxt "4500_Maya"
msgid "Well, since you asked so nicely, I could stay for a little while."
msgstr "Bueno, ya que lo pediste tan amablemente, podría quedarme un rato."

msgctxt "4512_Kiryu"
msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr "¿Estás segura?"

msgctxt "4524_Maya"
msgid "Yep. You're fun to talk to."
msgstr "Yep. You're fun to talk to."

msgctxt "4536_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. All right, then."
msgstr "Je. De acuerdo."

msgctxt "4548_Maya"
msgid "But you have to promise to come and see me every day, okay?"
msgstr "But you have to promise to come and see me every day, okay?"

msgctxt "4560_Kiryu"
msgid "I'll do my best."
msgstr "Dare lo mejor de mí."

msgctxt "4572_Maya"
msgid "I became friends with this girl recently, and we really hit it off. We have the same interests and everything."
msgstr "Recientemente, me hice amiga de esta chica, y realmente nos llevamos bien. Tenemos los mismos intereses."

msgctxt "4584_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh? That's nice."
msgstr "Oh, eso es bueno."

msgctxt "4596_Maya"
msgid "But we have totally different ideas about love. I don't get it."
msgstr "Pero tenemos ideas muy opuestas sobre el amor. No la entiendo."

msgctxt "4608_Kiryu"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿A qué te refieres?"

msgctxt "4620_Maya"
msgid "I think a woman should be devoted and try to stay next to her man as much as possible."
msgstr "Yo creo que una mujer debería dedicarse a intentar estar al lado de un hombre como sea posible."

msgctxt "4632_Maya"
msgid "But she says men get tired of that kind of thing and eventually leave you."
msgstr "Pero ella dice que los hombres se aburren de ese tipo de cosas y finalmente te abandonan."

msgctxt "4644_Kiryu"
msgid "I have to agree with her. Someone hanging around you all the time can be tiring."
msgstr "Estoy de acuerdo con ella. Alguien que siempre está junto a ti, todo el rato, llega a cansar."

msgctxt "4656_Maya"
msgid "What? You think so too?"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Tú también lo crees?"

msgctxt "4668_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. Don't get me wrong. If I love someone, I want to spend time with them. I just need time to myself, too."
msgstr "Sí. No me malinterpretes. Si amo a alguien, quiero pasar tiempo con ella. Pero yo también necesito tiempo para mí."

msgctxt "4680_Maya"
msgid "Well, I don't want to force myself on anyone."
msgstr "Bueno, no quiero obligar a nadie."

msgctxt "4692_Kiryu"
msgid "Then you should be fine."
msgstr "Entonces deberías estar bien."

msgctxt "4704_Maya"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr "¿De verdad?"

msgctxt "4716_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure. As long as you consider the man's feelings, you won't come off as selfish and needy."
msgstr "Mientras tengas en cuenta los sentimientos del hombre, no parecerás egoísta ni necesitada."

msgctxt "4728_Maya"
msgid "Okay. I guess you have to be devoted while still leaving a little space between you. It sounds a little tricky."
msgstr "Ok. Supongo que tienes que ser devoto y a la vez dejar un poco de espacio entre vosotros. Suena un poco difícil."

msgctxt "4740_Kiryu"
msgid "There's nothing wrong with being devoted. A man would be lucky to have such a woman."
msgstr "No hay nada de malo en que seas comprometida. Un hombre debería sentirse afortunado en tener ese tipo de mujer."

msgctxt "4752_Maya"
msgid "You agree with me?"
msgstr "¿Estás de acuerdo conmigo?"

msgctxt "4764_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure. It's much better than having a woman who cheats on you."
msgstr "Claro. Es mucho mejor que tener una mujer que te ponga los cuernos."

msgctxt "4776_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. You look like a ladies' man, but you're actually sweet, aren't you? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ji, ji. Pareces todo un casanova, pero, en realidad eres tierno, ¿no? <Color:7> ♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4788_Kiryu"
msgid "Can't I be both?"
msgstr "¿No puedo ser ambos?"

msgctxt "4800_Maya"
msgid "Ha! I hadn't thought of that! I guess that's possible."
msgstr "¡Ja! ¡No lo había pensado! Pero creo que es posible."

msgctxt "4812_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Good."
msgstr "Je. Está bien."

msgctxt "4824_Kiryu"
msgid "That's a tricky issue. It depends on what the man wants."
msgstr "Es... difícil de explicar. Todo depende de lo que el hombre quiera."

msgctxt "4836_Maya"
msgid "Ah, so you want to stay neutral, huh?"
msgstr "Ah, conque te pones neutral, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "4848_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh? What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿A qué se refiere?"

msgctxt "4860_Maya"
msgid "There must be a type of woman you prefer, right?"
msgstr "Debe haber un tipo de mujer que prefieras, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "4872_Kiryu"
msgid "Well..."
msgstr "Bueno..."

msgctxt "4884_Maya"
msgid "So, which is it?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿cuál es?"

msgctxt "4896_Kiryu"
msgid "I can't say. I like having a woman around, but sometimes I want to be alone. I can't choose between the two."
msgstr "I can't say. I like having a woman around, but sometimes I want to be alone. I can't choose between the two."

msgctxt "4908_Maya"
msgid "Oh. I didn't expect you to be so indecisive."
msgstr "Oh. I didn't expect you to be so indecisive."

msgctxt "4920_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "4932_Maya"
msgid "Ugh... I'm tired."
msgstr "Uf... Estoy cansada."

msgctxt "4944_Kiryu"
msgid "What's wrong?"
msgstr "¿Qué ocurre?"

msgctxt "4956_Maya"
msgid "Oh, I got stopped by a policeman on the way to work today."
msgstr "Oh, es que un policía me detuvo hoy de camino al trabajo."

msgctxt "4968_Maya"
msgid "I wasn't feeling well, so I wanted to tell him to get lost this time, but..."
msgstr "No me sentía bien, así que quería decirle que se perdiera esta vez, pero..."

msgctxt "4980_Kiryu"
msgid "This time? You get questioned that often?"
msgstr "¿Esta vez? ¿Te interrogan a menudo?"

msgctxt "4992_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. Do I look that suspicious to you?"
msgstr "Sí. ¿Crees que me veo sospechosa?"

msgctxt "5004_Kiryu"
msgid "Actually..."
msgstr "De hecho..."

msgctxt "5016_Maya"
msgid "Heh. Well, I'm pretty used to it by now. I'd get stopped every day when I was in junior high school."
msgstr "Je. Bueno, ya estoy acostumbrada. Me detenían todos los días mientras aún cursaba la secundaria."

msgctxt "5028_Kiryu"
msgid "Every day? Wow."
msgstr "¿Todos los días? Vaya..."

msgctxt "5040_Maya"
msgid "It's a lot better now. Maybe two or three times a month."
msgstr "Quizás exageré. Tal vez me detenían dos o tres veces al mes."

msgctxt "5052_Kiryu"
msgid "That's a pretty big difference."
msgstr "Eso es una gran diferencia."

msgctxt "5064_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. I think I don't stand out as much in Kamurocho."
msgstr "Sí, creo que no destaco tanto en Kamurocho."

msgctxt "5076_Kiryu"
msgid "But you still get stopped sometimes, so you must still stand out."
msgstr "Pero a veces te siguen deteniendo, así que debes seguir destacando."

msgctxt "5088_Maya"
msgid "Really? I like attention, but not that kind!"
msgstr "¿De verdad? Me gusta la atención, ¡pero no de ese tipo!"

msgctxt "5100_Kiryu"
msgid "You'd think the cops would stop bothering you once they remember your face."
msgstr "Uno pensaría que los policías dejarían de molestarte una vez que recuerdan tu cara."

msgctxt "5112_Maya"
msgid "I think I know their faces better than they know mine."
msgstr "Creo que conozco mejor sus caras mejor que la mía."

msgctxt "5124_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, oh well."
msgstr "Je, je, je..."

msgctxt "5136_Kiryu"
msgid "I get stopped sometimes myself."
msgstr "A veces yo mismo me detengo."

msgctxt "5148_Maya"
msgid "You do? Maybe we should start a club!"
msgstr "¿Lo haces? ¡Tal vez deberíamos crear un club!"

msgctxt "5160_Maya"
msgid "It must be because you have a wild and dangerous look about you."
msgstr "Eso debe ser porque tienes un aspecto salvaje y peligroso."

msgctxt "5172_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe. I usually just run away. I don't have the time."
msgstr "Tal vez. Por lo general, simplemente huyo. No tengo el tiempo."

msgctxt "5184_Maya"
msgid "But wouldn't that make you seem more suspicious?"
msgstr "Pero, ¿no te hace ver más sospechoso?"

msgctxt "5196_Kiryu"
msgid "That's why I make sure they don't catch me."
msgstr "Eso es porque casi nunca me atrapan."

msgctxt "5208_Maya"
msgid "Hahaha! It sounds like you're an expert. I should try running next time."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! Se ve que eres un experto. Deberías entrar en una maratón."

msgctxt "5220_Kiryu"
msgid "You could try to wear less flashy clothes. You do sort of stand out."
msgstr "Deberías usar ropa menos llamativa. De alguna manera te destacas."

msgctxt "5232_Maya"
msgid "But all the girls wear clothes like this."
msgstr "Pero todas las chicas se visten así."

msgctxt "5244_Kiryu"
msgid "So why do they stop you all the time?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿por qué te detienen todo el tiempo?"

msgctxt "5256_Maya"
msgid "I don't know. I guess I have some kind of suspicious aura."
msgstr "No lo sé. Supongo que causo sospechas."

msgctxt "5268_Kiryu"
msgid "They probably want an excuse to talk with a famous model."
msgstr "Probablemente, quieren una excusa para hablar con una modelo famosa."

msgctxt "5280_Maya"
msgid "Ha! You'll make me blush if you keep talking like that. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Ja! Me vas a sonrojar si sigues hablando así. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5292_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, sorry."
msgstr "Heh, sorry."

msgctxt "5304_Maya"
msgid "I hate arrogant men. You know, the kind of guy who acts like he knows you and bosses you around, even though you just met?"
msgstr "Odio a los hombres arrogantes. Ya sabes, ese tipo de persona que actúa como si fuera el jefe de todos y que te da órdenes, ¿Conoces a alguien así?"

msgctxt "5316_Kiryu"
msgid "You're not talking about me, are you?"
msgstr "¿No estarás hablando de mí?"

msgctxt "5328_Maya"
msgid "No, no. You're fine. A bit of swagger suits you."
msgstr "No, no. Usted está bien. A ti te va bien él fanfarroneó."

msgctxt "5340_Kiryu"
msgid "If you say so."
msgstr "¿Están listos?"

msgctxt "5352_Maya"
msgid "But a lot of guys these days are all talk. They think they're so special."
msgstr "Pero un montón de hombres son solo charlatanes. Piensan que son muy especiales."

msgctxt "5364_Kiryu"
msgid "They're fooling themselves. They think they're being cool."
msgstr "Se están engañando ellos mismo. Piensan que son geniales."

msgctxt "5376_Maya"
msgid "Right. They're trying so hard to impress girls, but it just ends up backfiring!"
msgstr "Verdad. Intenta impresionar a las chicas, ¡pero les sale el tiro por la culata!"

msgctxt "5388_Maya"
msgid "Being polite makes a much better impression."
msgstr "Ser cortés da una mejor impresión."

msgctxt "5400_Kiryu"
msgid "They're young. They don't know any better."
msgstr "Son jóvenes. No saben nada."

msgctxt "5412_Maya"
msgid "I'd take a polite older man over an arrogant young guy any day. They could learn a thing or two from you. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Preferiría a un hombre mayor cortés que a un joven arrogante común. Podría aprender un par de cosas de ti. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5424_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "5436_Kiryu"
msgid "Young guys don't know what manners are. If you don't know someone, you should make an effort to be polite."
msgstr "Los jóvenes no conocen los modales. Si no conoces a alguien así, debes de hacer el esfuerzo de ser cortés."

msgctxt "5448_Maya"
msgid "That's right! And it's not just young people. We get older customers like that, too."
msgstr "Así es. Y no solo los jóvenes. También tenemos clientes ancianos así."

msgctxt "5460_Maya"
msgid "They order us around like we're their servants or something!"
msgstr "¡Nos dan órdenes como si fuéramos sus sirvientas o algo así!"

msgctxt "5472_Kiryu"
msgid "I suppose one reason they come here is to blow off steam."
msgstr "Supongo que una de las razones por las que vienen aquí es para desahogarse."

msgctxt "5484_Maya"
msgid "I hate people who can only make themselves feel better by tearing other people down."
msgstr "Odio a la gente que solo puede sentirse mejor despreciando a los demás."

msgctxt "5496_Kiryu"
msgid "There's nothing you can do about it. Young guys don't have any accomplishments yet, so they try to make themselves look good."
msgstr "No hay nada que puedas hacer al respecto. Los jóvenes aún no tienen ningún logro, así que tratan de verse bien."

msgctxt "5508_Maya"
msgid "Why can't they just wait until they've got something real to brag about?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no pueden esperar a tener algo real de lo que presumir?"

msgctxt "5520_Kiryu"
msgid "Because they can't. If you look weak, the other guys eat you alive."
msgstr "Porque no pueden. Si pareces débil, los otros te comen vivo."

msgctxt "5532_Kiryu"
msgid "The first impression is particularly important. You have to take the initiative before the other guy does."
msgstr "La primera impresión es especialmente importante. Tienes que tomar la iniciativa antes de que el otro actúe."

msgctxt "5544_Maya"
msgid "So you agree with how those guys act? That's ridiculous."
msgstr "¿Así que estás de acuerdo con cómo actúan esos tipos? Eso es estúpido."

msgctxt "5556_Maya"
msgid "Even if they do have to be like that with other guys, it's a total turnoff for girls."
msgstr "Incluso si tienen que ser así con otros chicos, es un desinterés total para las chicas."

msgctxt "5568_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "5580_Maya"
msgid "My friend's boyfriend cheated on her. Again."
msgstr "El novio de mi amiga la volvió a engañar."

msgctxt "5592_Kiryu"
msgid "He's done it before?"
msgstr "¿Lo ha hecho antes?"

msgctxt "5604_Maya"
msgid "Yep. This would be the third time. She almost broke up with him last time, but he begged her to forgive him, so I guess she took him back."
msgstr "Sip. Ya debe ser como la tercera vez. Ella casi termina su relación, pero él estaba rogando para  que le perdonara, y acepto sus disculpas."

msgctxt "5616_Maya"
msgid "And now he's done it again! I can't believe it!"
msgstr "¡Y ahora lo volvió a hacer! ¡Es que no lo puedo creer!"

msgctxt "5628_Kiryu"
msgid "Hmm..."
msgstr "Mmm..."

msgctxt "5640_Maya"
msgid "I could never forgive that! Why do men have to cheat!?"
msgstr "¡Yo nunca lo perdonaría! ¿¡Por qué los hombres son mujeriegos!?"

msgctxt "5652_Kiryu"
msgid "You really want to know why men cheat?"
msgstr "¿En serio quieres saber por qué los hombres engañan?"

msgctxt "5664_Maya"
msgid "Yes!"
msgstr "¡Sí!"

msgctxt "5676_Kiryu"
msgid "But you said you could never forgive it. Does it matter what the reason is?"
msgstr "Pero dijiste que nunca podrías perdonarlo. ¿Importa cuál sea el motivo?"

msgctxt "5688_Maya"
msgid "Oh. I hadn't thought about it that way."
msgstr "Oh. No lo había pensado de esa manera."

msgctxt "5700_Maya"
msgid "But I'd still like to know!"
msgstr "¡Pero aun así me gustaría saberlo!"

msgctxt "5712_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, it depends. Sometimes it's the man's fault, and sometimes it's the woman's."
msgstr "Bueno, depende. A veces es culpa del hombre y a veces de la mujer."

msgctxt "5724_Maya"
msgid "Either way, I think they should make a clean break instead of cheating."
msgstr "En cualquier caso, creo que deberían hacer una ruptura honesta en lugar de engañar."

msgctxt "5736_Kiryu"
msgid "Yes, you're right."
msgstr "Sí, tienes toda la razón."

msgctxt "5748_Kiryu"
msgid "I don't know, but your friend's relationship isn't healthy. She should leave him."
msgstr "No lo sé, pero la relación de tu amigo no es sana. Ella debería de dejarlo definitivamente."

msgctxt "5760_Maya"
msgid "You're right. I'd have broken up with him after the first time."
msgstr "Tienes toda la razón. Yo habría roto después de la primera vez."

msgctxt "5772_Kiryu"
msgid "Once and it's over?"
msgstr "¿Una vez y se acabó?"

msgctxt "5784_Maya"
msgid "Yes. I can't forgive that kind of betrayal."
msgstr "Sí. No podría perdonar tal acto de traición."

msgctxt "5796_Kiryu"
msgid "So you'd never cheat yourself, right?"
msgstr "Así que nunca te engañarías a ti misma, ¿no?"

msgctxt "5808_Maya"
msgid "Of course not. I'm a devoted girlfriend."
msgstr "Por supuesto que no. Soy una novia leal."

msgctxt "5820_Kiryu"
msgid "Good. I'd be reassured if I was your boyfriend."
msgstr "Bien. Me calmaría si yo fuera tu novio."

msgctxt "5832_Maya"
msgid "Thank you. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Gracias. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5844_Kiryu"
msgid "It shows that he's a real man. Your friend should be proud that her man can get that many girls."
msgstr "Él solo está demostrando su hombría. Esa tipa debería estar totalmente orgullosa de que su macho pueda conseguir un montón de mujeres."

msgctxt "5856_Maya"
msgid "What the hell are you talking about!?"
msgstr "¿¡De qué carajos estás hablando!?"

msgctxt "5868_Kiryu"
msgid "It takes money to date a girl. Just think how much it takes to date several girls at once."
msgstr "Se ocupa dinero para salir con una chica. Ahora imagínate cuanto costará salir con varias chicas a la vez."

msgctxt "5880_Kiryu"
msgid "Your friend managed to land a guy who has that kind of resources. She should be happy."
msgstr "Tu amiga consiguió un macho con esos recursos. Debería estar contenta."

msgctxt "5892_Maya"
msgid "I can't believe you! Trying to justify it is even worse than sneaking around!"
msgstr "¡No lo puedo creer! ¡Engañar a una mujer es una cosa, pero justificarlo es incluso peor! "

msgctxt "5904_Maya"
msgid "I really thought you'd understand, too..."
msgstr "No lo entenderías..."

msgctxt "5916_Maya"
msgid "You look like a strong drinker."
msgstr "Pareces ser un bebedor muy fuerte."

msgctxt "5928_Kiryu"
msgid "I suppose I am. What about you?"
msgstr "Supongo que lo soy. ¿Qué hay de ti?"

msgctxt "5940_Maya"
msgid "Me? I'm a lightweight. I like alcohol, though."
msgstr "¿Yo? Soy ligera. Sin embargo, me gusta el alcohol."

msgctxt "5952_Maya"
msgid "I wish I could become a stronger drinker."
msgstr "Desearía aguantar mucho más el alcohol."

msgctxt "5964_Kiryu"
msgid "They have medicine for that, you know. You can take it before you drink."
msgstr "Existen medicamentos para eso, ya sabes. Lo puedes tomar antes de beber."

msgctxt "5976_Maya"
msgid "I've heard of that. Sort of the same idea as antacid, right? Maybe I'll try it!"
msgstr "Escuche hablar de eso. Es algo similar a los antiácidos, ¿verdad? ¡Tal vez lo pruebe!"

msgctxt "5988_Kiryu"
msgid "You could also try tomato juice. It helps your body break down alcohol."
msgstr "También deberías probar el jugo de tomate. Eso ayuda a descomponer el alcohol."

msgctxt "6000_Maya"
msgid "Wow. You know a lot about this."
msgstr "Vaya. Sabes mucho de estas cosas."

msgctxt "6012_Kiryu"
msgid "Any serious drinker has to know how to sober up."
msgstr "Cualquier bebedor empedernido debe de saber como recuperar la sobriedad."

msgctxt "6024_Maya"
msgid "A gentleman and a strong drinker. That's just wonderful. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Un caballero y un bebedor fuerte. Esto es simplemente maravilloso. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "6036_Kiryu"
msgid "Some people just can't drink. Your body just doesn't break down alcohol as well as other people."
msgstr "Algunas personas simplemente no pueden beber, su cuerpo no descompone el alcohol tan bien como a otras personas."

msgctxt "6048_Maya"
msgid "So I'm just stuck like this?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿estoy atrapada así?"

msgctxt "6060_Kiryu"
msgid "You can drink a little bit, right? Why not be satisfied with that?"
msgstr "Puedes beber un poco, ¿no? ¿Por qué no conformarse con eso?"

msgctxt "6072_Maya"
msgid "It's no fun. I want to be able to drink with my friends."
msgstr "No tiene chiste. Quiero poder beber con mis amigos."

msgctxt "6084_Kiryu"
msgid "But there's no real benefit to drinking. It costs money, and you could become addicted if you're not careful."
msgstr "Pero beber no tiene ningún beneficio real. Cuesta dinero y puedes volverte adicta si no tienes cuidado."

msgctxt "6096_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, I guess you're right."
msgstr "Sí, supongo que tienes razón."

msgctxt "6108_Kiryu"
msgid "Try drinking more slowly. That way you can keep drinking for as long as your friends are."
msgstr "Intenta beber más despacio. Con eso podrás beber por más tiempo junto a tus amigos."

msgctxt "6120_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, that's pretty much my only choice."
msgstr "Sí, esa es casi mi única opción."

msgctxt "6132_Kiryu"
msgid "You just need to know your limits."
msgstr "Solo hay que conocer los límites."

msgctxt "6144_Kiryu"
msgid "And that's true for strong drinkers, too. Anyone can make the mistake of drinking too much."
msgstr "Y eso también es cierto para los bebedores empedernidos. Cualquiera puede cometer el error de beber demasiado."

msgctxt "6156_Maya"
msgid "I guess you're right. I'd rather drink slowly and enjoy myself than drink a lot and get sick."
msgstr "Supongo que tienes razón. Prefiero beber despacio y disfrutar que beber mucho y caer enferma."

msgctxt "6168_Kiryu"
msgid "It takes experience to know how to drink, but you'll get it eventually."
msgstr "Hace falta experiencia para saber beber, pero al final lo conseguirás."

msgctxt "6180_Maya"
msgid "Yes. Thanks for your help!"
msgstr "Yes. Thanks for your help!"

msgctxt "6192_Maya"
msgid "My friends get mad at me for saying the same things over and over again."
msgstr "Mis amigos se enojan conmigo por decir las mismas cosas una y otra vez."

msgctxt "6204_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh? Like what?"
msgstr "¿Oh? ¿Como cuales?"

msgctxt "6216_Maya"
msgid "Well, today I asked my friend if she had eaten yet, and she said she had a hamburger."
msgstr "Hoy le he preguntado a mi amiga si ya había comido y me ha dicho que había comido una hamburguesa."

msgctxt "6228_Maya"
msgid "Ten minutes later, I was like, \"So, have you eaten yet?\" And she was like, \"I told you, I had a hamburger!\""
msgstr "Diez minutos después, le dije: \"¿Ya comiste algo?\" Y ella me dijo: \"¡Ya te lo dije, me comí una hamburguesa!\""

msgctxt "6240_Kiryu"
msgid "That's pretty bad."
msgstr "Eso es bastante malo."

msgctxt "6252_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. They get mad because they think I'm not really listening."
msgstr "¡Sí! Ellas se enojan porque piensan que no las escucho."

msgctxt "6264_Kiryu"
msgid "You must have a bad memory."
msgstr "Debes de tener mala memoria."

msgctxt "6276_Maya"
msgid "Hmm. I don't think I do..."
msgstr "Mmm. No creo poder hacerlo..."

msgctxt "6288_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you remember what we talked about the last time I was here?"
msgstr "¿Recuerdas lo que hablamos la última vez que estuve aquí?"

msgctxt "6300_Maya"
msgid "Huh!? I..."
msgstr "¿Eh? Yo..."

msgctxt "6312_Kiryu"
msgid "Come on. What'd we talk about?"
msgstr "Anda. ¿De qué hablamos?"

msgctxt "6324_Maya"
msgid "Um..."
msgstr "Em..."

msgctxt "6336_Maya"
msgid "Sorry, I can't remember! Hahaha!"
msgstr "Perdón, ¡No recuerdo nadita! ¡Ja, ja, ja!"

msgctxt "6348_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh. Now I'm starting to get mad, too."
msgstr "Eh. Ya empiezo a irritarme."

msgctxt "6360_Kiryu"
msgid "It is kinda rude. You need to pay attention to what your friends are saying, especially if you're the one asking them the question."
msgstr "Eso es un poco grosero. Tienes que prestar atención a lo que dicen tus amigos, sobre todo si eres tú quien les hace la pregunta."

msgctxt "6372_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. I guess it is rude."
msgstr "Sí. Supongo que es grosero."

msgctxt "6384_Kiryu"
msgid "Is that really what's happening? Are you not listening?"
msgstr "¿Es eso lo que está pasando? ¿No escuchas?"

msgctxt "6396_Maya"
msgid "Well, it doesn't happen when we're talking about something important. Maybe I don't pay enough attention to trivial things."
msgstr "Bueno, no ocurre cuando hablamos de algo importante. Quizá no le presto suficiente atención a las trivialidades."

msgctxt "6408_Kiryu"
msgid "I feel a little sorry for your friends, then."
msgstr "Siento un poco de lástima por tus amigos."

msgctxt "6420_Maya"
msgid "Haha! I should be more careful in conversation."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja! Debería ser más cuidadosa en las conversaciones."

msgctxt "6432_Kiryu"
msgid "Good luck with that."
msgstr "Buena suerte con eso."

msgctxt "6444_Kiryu"
msgid "You already told me about this."
msgstr "Pero ya me estás hablando de esto."

msgctxt "6456_Maya"
msgid "Huh!? I did!? Oh no, it happened again!"
msgstr "¿¡Eh!? ¿¡Lo hice!? ¡Caramba, ha vuelto a pasar!"

msgctxt "6468_Kiryu"
msgid "Just kidding."
msgstr "Es broma."

msgctxt "6480_Maya"
msgid "What!? Why you! Don't scare me like that!"
msgstr "¿¡Qué!? ¡No me asustes así!"

msgctxt "6492_Kiryu"
msgid "Haha. It sounds like you really don't know what you've talked about before."
msgstr "Ja, ja. Parece que realmente no sabes de lo que has hablado antes."

msgctxt "6504_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, you're right. Maybe I've got a bad memory."
msgstr "Sí, tienes razón. Es posible que tenga mala memoria."

msgctxt "6516_Kiryu"
msgid "If you tell me about this again, we'll know."
msgstr "If you tell me about this again, we'll know."

msgctxt "6528_Maya"
msgid "Then I'd better be extra careful not to mention this again!"
msgstr "Then I'd better be extra careful not to mention this again!"

msgctxt "6540_Maya"
msgid "I wish I had a driver's license."
msgstr "Desearía tener una licencia para conducir."

msgctxt "6552_Kiryu"
msgid "You don't have one? Well, you can go to driving school."
msgstr "¿No tienes una? Bueno, siempre puedes ir a la escuela de manejo."

msgctxt "6564_Maya"
msgid "I went once, but I took too long, so they kicked me out."
msgstr "Fui una vez, pero tardé mucho y me echaron."

msgctxt "6576_Kiryu"
msgid "Why'd you take so long?"
msgstr "¿Por qué te tardaste tanto?"

msgctxt "6588_Maya"
msgid "I was too busy. I couldn't find the time to go to school."
msgstr "Estaba muy ocupada. No encontraba el tiempo para ir a la escuela."

msgctxt "6600_Kiryu"
msgid "Ah. That makes sense."
msgstr "Oh. Eso tiene sentido."

msgctxt "6612_Maya"
msgid "It's kinda strange for a girl my age to not have a license, huh? I just don't want to go back to driving school."
msgstr "Es raro que una chica de mi edad no tenga carnet, ¿verdad? No quiero volver a la escuela de manejo."

msgctxt "6624_Kiryu"
msgid "You should get one when you get the chance. Who knows when you might need a license?"
msgstr "Deberías conseguir una cuando tengas la oportunidad. ¿Quién sabe cuándo podrías necesitar una licencia?"

msgctxt "6636_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, that's a good point. I should make the time to go, huh?"
msgstr "Sí, es un buen punto. Debería dedicar mi tiempo para ir, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "6648_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. Will you buy a car when you get your license?"
msgstr "Sí. ¿Te comprarás un coche cuando te saques la licencia?"

msgctxt "6660_Maya"
msgid "I want one, but going to driving school costs money too. I'll probably have to wait a while."
msgstr "Quiero uno, pero ir a la escuela de manejo también cuesta dinero. Quizá tenga que esperar un tiempo."

msgctxt "6672_Kiryu"
msgid "So getting a license is just the first step."
msgstr "Obtener una licencia es solo el primer paso."

msgctxt "6684_Maya"
msgid "That's right. Okay, I'm really gonna do it this time!"
msgstr "Así es. De acuerdo, ¡esta vez lo voy a hacer de verdad!"

msgctxt "6696_Kiryu"
msgid "If your boyfriend can drive, you don't need a license."
msgstr "Si tu novio puede conducir, no necesitas una licencia."

msgctxt "6708_Maya"
msgid "But I want to drive myself! And sometimes I need to go shopping."
msgstr "Pero yo quiero conducir. Además, necesito ir de compras."

msgctxt "6720_Kiryu"
msgid "Go shopping with your boyfriend. You can get him to treat you to dinner, too."
msgstr "Vete de compras con tu novio. También puedes conseguir que te invite a cenar."

msgctxt "6732_Maya"
msgid "Um, I know some girls focus on the size of a man's wallet, but I'm not like that."
msgstr "Sé que algunas chicas se fijan en el tamaño de la cartera de un hombre, pero yo no soy así."

msgctxt "6744_Maya"
msgid "And if I have enough free time to get a boyfriend, I have enough time to get my license instead."
msgstr "Y si tengo tiempo libre para tener pareja, también lo tengo para sacarme la licencia."

msgctxt "6756_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "Oh."

msgctxt "6768_Kiryu"
msgid "Driving schools can be expensive. I understand why you don't want to go back."
msgstr "Las escuelas de manejo pueden ser caras."

msgctxt "6780_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. I wonder if there's some kind of discount I could get."
msgstr "Exacto. Me pregunto si hay algún tipo de descuento que pueda obtener."

msgctxt "6792_Kiryu"
msgid "And even after you get your license, it can be expensive to own a car. You'd need to make some changes in your life."
msgstr "E incluso después de sacarte la licencia, puede resultar caro tener un coche. Tendrías que hacer algunos cambios en tu vida."

msgctxt "6804_Maya"
msgid "True..."
msgstr "Cierto..."

msgctxt "6816_Maya"
msgid "But having a car would change my life in other ways. I could go for drives whenever I wanted."
msgstr "Pero tener un coche cambiaría mi vida de otras maneras. Podría salir a dar una vuelta siempre que quisiera."

msgctxt "6828_Kiryu"
msgid "And there are places that are hard to get to by train."
msgstr "Y hay lugares a los que son difíciles de llegar en tren."

msgctxt "6840_Maya"
msgid "The more I talk about it, the more I want to get a license after all. Maybe I will go back to driving school."
msgstr "Cuanto más hablo de ello, más ganas tengo de sacarme la licencia después de todo. Quizá vuelva a la escuela de manejo."

msgctxt "6852_Maya"
msgid "Uh-oh."
msgstr "Oh-ou."

msgctxt "6864_Kiryu"
msgid "What's wrong?"
msgstr "¿Qué ocurre?"

msgctxt "6876_Maya"
msgid "My friend sent me the funniest picture yesterday. I wanted to show it to you, but I think I deleted it."
msgstr "Mi amiga me envió una foto muy divertida ayer. Quería mostrártela, pero creo que la borre."

msgctxt "6888_Kiryu"
msgid "What kind of picture was it?"
msgstr "¿Qué clase de foto era esa?"

msgctxt "6900_Maya"
msgid "I was standing on top of a bar with a backpack or something on my back."
msgstr "Estaba encima de una barra con una mochila o algo así a la espalda."

msgctxt "6912_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Were you drunk?"
msgstr "Je. ¿Estabas ebria?"

msgctxt "6924_Maya"
msgid "I think so. I don't remember it at all."
msgstr "Eso creo. No recuerdo nada."

msgctxt "6936_Kiryu"
msgid "I thought you didn't drink much."
msgstr "Pensaba que no bebías mucho."

msgctxt "6948_Maya"
msgid "Oh, it was from last year. I don't know why she just sent it to me now."
msgstr "Oh, era del año pasado. No entiendo por qué me lo acaba de enviar ahora."

msgctxt "6960_Kiryu"
msgid "See if she can send it to you again. I'd like to see it for myself."
msgstr "A ver si te lo puede enviar otra vez. Me gustaría verlo por mí mismo."

msgctxt "6972_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. I'm warning you now, it's pretty funny."
msgstr "Je, je. Te lo advierto ahora, es bastante chistoso."

msgctxt "6984_Maya"
msgid "The first time I saw it, I thought, \"What the hell is this girl doing!?\""
msgstr "La primera vez que la vi, pensé: \"¿Qué demonios está haciendo esta chica?\"."

msgctxt "6996_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Now I really have to see it."
msgstr "Je. Ahora sí que tengo que verla."

msgctxt "7008_Kiryu"
msgid "Why don't you forward it directly to my phone?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no lo reenvías directamente a mi teléfono?"

msgctxt "7020_Maya"
msgid "No way! Then you'll keep it forever! I'll show it to you, but just once!"
msgstr "¡Nunca! ¡Entonces te lo quedarás para siempre! ¡Te lo enseñaré, pero solo una vez!"

msgctxt "7032_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Fine."
msgstr "Je. Está bien"

msgctxt "7044_Kiryu"
msgid "You used to get drunk a lot? Not many people would climb onto a bar, even if they were drunk."
msgstr "¿Solías beber mucho? No mucha gente se subía a una barra, aunque estuviera borracha."

msgctxt "7056_Maya"
msgid "You're probably right. I could've gotten in trouble."
msgstr "Probablemente tengas razón. Podría haberme metido en problemas."

msgctxt "7068_Kiryu"
msgid "You're lucky you didn't get banned."
msgstr "Tienes suerte de que no te hayan vetado."

msgctxt "7080_Maya"
msgid "And why was my friend taking that picture? She should've stopped me."
msgstr "¿Y por qué estaba mi amiga sacando esa foto? Ella debería haberme frenado."

msgctxt "7092_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Must be because you're a model and all."
msgstr "Je. Debe ser porque eres modelo y todo eso."

msgctxt "7104_Maya"
msgid "Is that supposed to be a compliment?"
msgstr "¿Eso es un cumplido?"

msgctxt "7116_Kiryu"
msgid "A backpack? Were you traveling?"
msgstr "¿Una mochila? ¿Andabas de viaje?"

msgctxt "7128_Maya"
msgid "Oh no, it wasn't mine. I think it belonged to somebody else at the bar."
msgstr "Ah, no, eso no era mío. Creo que era de otra persona en el bar."

msgctxt "7140_Kiryu"
msgid "But why were you wearing it?"
msgstr "Pero, ¿por qué lo llevabas puesto?"

msgctxt "7152_Maya"
msgid "Uh, that's hard to say."
msgstr "Bueno... es complicado de decir."

msgctxt "7164_Maya"
msgid "When I get drunk, I like to wear anything I can get my hands on. Bags, jewelry, other people's clothes..."
msgstr "Cuando me embriago, me gusta ponerme cualquier cosa que caiga en mis manos. Bolsos, joyas, ropa de otras personas..."

msgctxt "7176_Kiryu"
msgid "That sounds like a problem."
msgstr "Eso suena a problemas."

msgctxt "7188_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe you could put a lot of clothes on before you get drunk?"
msgstr "¿Podrías ponerte mucha ropa antes de emborracharte?"

msgctxt "7200_Maya"
msgid "Haha! That just might work."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja! Eso podría funcionar."

msgctxt "7212_Maya"
msgid "But I don't drink too much nowadays, so it's not a big deal anymore."
msgstr "Pero ya no bebo mucho, así que no es un problema."

msgctxt "7224_Maya"
msgid "Do you go to Yokohama very often?"
msgstr "Do you go to Yokohama very often?"

msgctxt "7236_Kiryu"
msgid "Not really."
msgstr "En realidad, no."

msgctxt "7248_Maya"
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "Oh."

msgctxt "7260_Kiryu"
msgid "Why do you ask?"
msgstr "Why do you ask?"

msgctxt "7272_Maya"
msgid "I'm from Yokohama."
msgstr "I'm from Yokohama."

msgctxt "7284_Kiryu"
msgid "You are? It's certainly a nice city."
msgstr "You are? It's certainly a nice city."

msgctxt "7296_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. It's also a great place for dates."
msgstr "Yeah. It's also a great place for dates."

msgctxt "7308_Kiryu"
msgid "True. There are a lot of date spots there."
msgstr "True. There are a lot of date spots there."

msgctxt "7320_Maya"
msgid "I'm not just talking about the famous places. There are lots of spots only the locals know."
msgstr "I'm not just talking about the famous places. There are lots of spots only the locals know."

msgctxt "7332_Kiryu"
msgid "You go on a lot of dates then?"
msgstr "You go on a lot of dates then?"

msgctxt "7344_Maya"
msgid "Hmm? Do I detect a hint of jealousy?"
msgstr "Hmm? Do I detect a hint of jealousy?"

msgctxt "7356_Kiryu"
msgid "That's not how I meant it. You just sounded like you knew a lot about it."
msgstr "That's not how I meant it. You just sounded like you knew a lot about it."

msgctxt "7368_Maya"
msgid "Come on. You don't have to be embarrassed."
msgstr "Come on. You don't have to be embarrassed."

msgctxt "7380_Maya"
msgid "Don't you know of any places like that? Special places to take your girlfriend?"
msgstr "Don't you know of any places like that? Special places to take your girlfriend?"

msgctxt "7392_Kiryu"
msgid "No."
msgstr "Así es."

msgctxt "7404_Maya"
msgid "Oh. Well, I should show you mine! They have my seal of approval!"
msgstr "Oh. Well, I should show you mine! They have my seal of approval!"

msgctxt "7416_Kiryu"
msgid "I'd like that."
msgstr "Eso me gustaría."

msgctxt "7428_Kiryu"
msgid "Wouldn't you stand out more there? If all the locals know about it..."
msgstr "Wouldn't you stand out more there? If all the locals know about it..."

msgctxt "7440_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, that's true. I do seem to run into friends a lot when there."
msgstr "Yeah, that's true. I do seem to run into friends a lot when there."

msgctxt "7452_Kiryu"
msgid "Then everybody knows who is dating whom. And where they go. Wouldn't it be better if you went somewhere private?"
msgstr "Then everybody knows who is dating whom. And where they go. Wouldn't it be better if you went somewhere private?"

msgctxt "7464_Maya"
msgid "I don't need to sneak around my own hometown!"
msgstr "I don't need to sneak around my own hometown!"

msgctxt "7476_Maya"
msgid "Or do you not want to be seen with the people you go out with?"
msgstr "Or do you not want to be seen with the people you go out with?"

msgctxt "7488_Kiryu"
msgid "Uh, that's not what I meant at all."
msgstr "Uh, that's not what I meant at all."

msgctxt "7500_Maya"
msgid "I'm a little disappointed. I was going to tell you about this great place, but never mind."
msgstr "I'm a little disappointed. I was going to tell you about this great place, but never mind."

msgctxt "7512_Kiryu"
msgid "Wha...?"
msgstr "Wha...?"

msgctxt "7524_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe you can show me sometime. I'd like to see what these places are like."
msgstr "Maybe you can show me sometime. I'd like to see what these places are like."

msgctxt "7536_Maya"
msgid "Um... Does that mean you want to go out on a date with me?"
msgstr "Um... Does that mean you want to go out on a date with me?"

msgctxt "7548_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure does."
msgstr "Sure does."

msgctxt "7560_Maya"
msgid "Oh, I don't know. I don't take just anyone to these places. They're special to me."
msgstr "Oh, I don't know. I don't take just anyone to these places. They're special to me."

msgctxt "7572_Kiryu"
msgid "You're the one who brought them up."
msgstr "You're the one who brought them up."

msgctxt "7584_Maya"
msgid "Ha, that's true."
msgstr "Ha, that's true."

msgctxt "7596_Maya"
msgid "All right. Once I know you a little better, I can show you my favorite dating spots."
msgstr "All right. Once I know you a little better, I can show you my favorite dating spots."

msgctxt "7608_Kiryu"
msgid "I look forward to it."
msgstr "Lo estaré esperando."

msgctxt "7620_Maya"
msgid "I had a modeling job today. I wore some of the cutest outfits!"
msgstr "I had a modeling job today. I wore some of the cutest outfits!"

msgctxt "7632_Kiryu"
msgid "That's good. It must be tough to have two jobs, though."
msgstr "That's good. It must be tough to have two jobs, though."

msgctxt "7644_Maya"
msgid "Kinda. But modeling's not so bad this time of year. It's terrible in the summer and winter."
msgstr "Kinda. But modeling's not so bad this time of year. It's terrible in the summer and winter."

msgctxt "7656_Kiryu"
msgid "Why's that?"
msgstr "¿Por qué?"

msgctxt "7668_Maya"
msgid "They always start selling seasonal clothes a bit early, and we have to do the photoshoots even earlier."
msgstr "They always start selling seasonal clothes a bit early, and we have to do the photoshoots even earlier."

msgctxt "7680_Maya"
msgid "So we're posing in light summer clothes in the winter and in hot winter clothes in the middle of summer."
msgstr "So we're posing in light summer clothes in the winter and in hot winter clothes in the middle of summer."

msgctxt "7692_Kiryu"
msgid "That does sound terrible. And you have to look happy for the cameras, right?"
msgstr "That does sound terrible. And you have to look happy for the cameras, right?"

msgctxt "7704_Maya"
msgid "That's right. If the shoot lasts too long in the summer, I start to sweat."
msgstr "That's right. If the shoot lasts too long in the summer, I start to sweat."

msgctxt "7716_Kiryu"
msgid "Why don't they just do it indoors?"
msgstr "Why don't they just do it indoors?"

msgctxt "7728_Maya"
msgid "Sometimes they do. I'm pretty used to it either way."
msgstr "Sometimes they do. I'm pretty used to it either way."

msgctxt "7740_Kiryu"
msgid "Okay. Well, good luck."
msgstr "Okay. Well, good luck."

msgctxt "7752_Kiryu"
msgid "They really start that early? How do they know what's going to be popular?"
msgstr "They really start that early? How do they know what's going to be popular?"

msgctxt "7764_Maya"
msgid "What? Oh, haha! You don't understand, do you? They don't have to know."
msgstr "What? Oh, haha! You don't understand, do you? They don't have to know."

msgctxt "7776_Kiryu"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿A qué te refieres?"

msgctxt "7788_Maya"
msgid "It's the fashion industry that makes the trends. They decide what's going to be popular before they do the photoshoot."
msgstr "It's the fashion industry that makes the trends. They decide what's going to be popular before they do the photoshoot."

msgctxt "7800_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, I see. You must know what's going to be popular next season, then."
msgstr "Oh, I see. You must know what's going to be popular next season, then."

msgctxt "7812_Maya"
msgid "Yep! That's why models like me are called trendsetters!"
msgstr "Yep! That's why models like me are called trendsetters!"

msgctxt "7824_Kiryu"
msgid "Haha."
msgstr "Ja, ja."

msgctxt "7836_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm surprised you don't get sick. Wouldn't you catch a cold in the winter?"
msgstr "I'm surprised you don't get sick. Wouldn't you catch a cold in the winter?"

msgctxt "7848_Maya"
msgid "Well, I'm pretty used to it by now. I guess it's not that big of a deal."
msgstr "Well, I'm pretty used to it by now. I guess it's not that big of a deal."

msgctxt "7860_Maya"
msgid "What's worse is having to get up so early on the day of a shoot."
msgstr "What's worse is having to get up so early on the day of a shoot."

msgctxt "7872_Kiryu"
msgid "That's not so bad. You just have to go to bed early."
msgstr "That's not so bad. You just have to go to bed early."

msgctxt "7884_Maya"
msgid "I do go to bed early! But then I can't go out with my friends. That's the problem."
msgstr "I do go to bed early! But then I can't go out with my friends. That's the problem."

msgctxt "7896_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. A lot of people have that kind of problem."
msgstr "Heh. A lot of people have that kind of problem."

msgctxt "7908_Maya"
msgid "Can I ask you something?"
msgstr "Akiyama-san. ¿Puedo preguntarle algo?"

msgctxt "7920_Kiryu"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "7932_Maya"
msgid "When two people start going out, it's normal for them to say \"I love you\" to each other, right?"
msgstr "Cuando dos personas empiezan a salir, es normal que se digan \"te amo\", ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "7944_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm not sure. In what kind of situation?"
msgstr "No estoy seguro. ¿Y en qué tipo de situación puede suceder?"

msgctxt "7956_Maya"
msgid "Any situation. When you're holding hands, hugging each other, or whatever. People say \"I love you\" pretty often, right?"
msgstr "En cualquier situación. Cuando se dan las manos, cuando se abrazan o lo que sea. La gente dice \"te amo\" muy a menudo, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "7968_Kiryu"
msgid "That's cute. Yeah, some people do that when they first start dating."
msgstr "Eso es lindo. Sí, algunas personas hacen eso cuando empiezan a salir."

msgctxt "7980_Maya"
msgid "I thought so. I even say it after I've been dating someone for a long time."
msgstr "Eso pensaba yo. Incluso lo digo después de haber estado saliendo con alguien durante mucho tiempo."

msgctxt "7992_Kiryu"
msgid "If you stop saying it, it usually means you're getting tired of them."
msgstr "Si dejas de decirlo, suele significar que estás cansado de ellos."

msgctxt "8004_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. I hate it when I say \"I love you\" and the guy gives some sort of vague response."
msgstr "Sí. Odio cuando digo \"te amo\" y el tipo me da una respuesta vacía."

msgctxt "8016_Maya"
msgid "You'd say \"I love you, too\" even if you've been dating for a long time, wouldn't you?"
msgstr "Dirías \"yo también te amo\" aunque llevaran mucho tiempo saliendo, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "8028_Kiryu"
msgid "We'll have to wait and see."
msgstr "Tendremos que esperar y ver."

msgctxt "8040_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe those lovey-dovey couples do. It's embarrassing to see."
msgstr "Tal vez esas parejas enamoradas lo hacen. Es vergonzoso, de verdad."

msgctxt "8052_Maya"
msgid "Hmph!"
msgstr "¡Mmpf!"

msgctxt "8064_Maya"
msgid "What's so wrong with being in love!?"
msgstr "¿¡Qué tiene de malo estar enamorada!?"

msgctxt "8076_Kiryu"
msgid "I don't like watching others act like lovesick kids."
msgstr "No me gusta ver a los demás actuar como niños enamorados."

msgctxt "8088_Maya"
msgid "But if the couple's happy, what's wrong with it? They're not hurting anybody."
msgstr "Pero si la pareja es feliz, ¿qué tiene de malo? No hacen daño a nadie."

msgctxt "8100_Kiryu"
msgid "It takes more than saying you love someone to be happy, you know."
msgstr "¿Sabes? Hace falta algo más que decir que quieres a alguien para ser feliz."

msgctxt "8112_Maya"
msgid "You just don't get it, do you?"
msgstr "No lo entiendes, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "8124_Kiryu"
msgid "Is it really necessary to say it? You don't need words to express how you feel."
msgstr "¿Realmente es necesario decir eso? No necesitas palabras para expresar lo que sientes."

msgctxt "8136_Maya"
msgid "Yes, you do!"
msgstr "Sí, ¡totalmente necesario!"

msgctxt "8148_Maya"
msgid "When you tell each other you love one another, it reaffirms your feelings."
msgstr "Cuando se dicen que se quieren, se reafirman sus propios sentimientos."

msgctxt "8160_Kiryu"
msgid "You'd be worried if you weren't reassured that you love each other?"
msgstr "¿Estarías preocupado si no te aseguraran que se quieren?"

msgctxt "8172_Maya"
msgid "Well, no. I didn't mean that, exactly."
msgstr "Bueno, no. No quise decir eso."

msgctxt "8184_Kiryu"
msgid "If you really love another person, being close to them should be enough. You should even feel a connection when you're apart."
msgstr "Si realmente amas a otra persona, estar cerca de ella debería ser suficiente. Incluso deberías sentir una conexión cuando están separados."

msgctxt "8196_Maya"
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "Oh."

msgctxt "8208_Maya"
msgid "Now that you put it that way, I think you might be right. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Now that you put it that way, I think you might be right. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8220_Maya"
msgid "Do you remember that policeman who stopped me while we were on our date?"
msgstr "¿Recuerdas al policía que me detuvo mientras estábamos en nuestra cita?"

msgctxt "8232_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "8244_Maya"
msgid "I ran into him again not long after that."
msgstr "Me encontré con él de nuevo, no mucho después."

msgctxt "8256_Kiryu"
msgid "He questioned you again?"
msgstr "¿Y te interrogó nuevamente?"

msgctxt "8268_Maya"
msgid "No. Actually, he was being friendly."
msgstr "No. En realidad, estaba siendo amigable."

msgctxt "8280_Maya"
msgid "He said he was getting off duty soon and asked if I wanted to go for coffee. He was trying to pick me up!"
msgstr "Me dijo que pronto saldría de servicio y me preguntó si quería ir a tomar un cafecito. ¡Intentaba ligar conmigo!"

msgctxt "8292_Kiryu"
msgid "Really? I never thought a cop would try something like that while he was on duty."
msgstr "¿¡En serio!? Nunca pensé que un policía haría algo así mientras estaba de servicio."

msgctxt "8304_Maya"
msgid "Hahaha! It was kind of funny, so I let him buy me some."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! Me hizo gracia, así que le dejé que me comprara algo."

msgctxt "8316_Kiryu"
msgid "Don't tell me you like this guy."
msgstr "No me digas que te gusta ese tipo."

msgctxt "8328_Maya"
msgid "Haha! No, not at all."
msgstr "Ja, ja. Para nada."

msgctxt "8340_Kiryu"
msgid "Then why'd you go out with him?"
msgstr "¿Y por qué saliste con él?"

msgctxt "8352_Maya"
msgid "Huh? I had a little free time, so I thought I'd be nice to him."
msgstr "¿Eh? Tenía tiempo libre, así que pensé en ser amable con él."

msgctxt "8364_Kiryu"
msgid "What's so fun about going out with somebody you don't even like?"
msgstr "¿Qué tiene de divertido salir con alguien que ni siquiera te gusta?"

msgctxt "8376_Maya"
msgid "Well, it wasn't really much fun. He kept asking all of these questions. Like, did I have a boyfriend?"
msgstr "Bueno, en realidad no fue muy divertido. No paraba de hacer preguntas. Como, ¿tienes novio?"

msgctxt "8388_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh."
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "8400_Maya"
msgid "It's okay. I won't see him again. You don't have to worry. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "It's okay. I won't see him again. You don't have to worry. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8412_Kiryu"
msgid "I wasn't really worried..."
msgstr "No estaba preocupado..."

msgctxt "8424_Kiryu"
msgid "So you went out with him? Just like that?"
msgstr "¿Así que saliste con él? ¿Así sin más?"

msgctxt "8436_Maya"
msgid "Why not? He's a cop. I figured I'd at least be safe."
msgstr "¿Por qué no? Es policía. Pensé que al menos estaría segura."

msgctxt "8448_Kiryu"
msgid "There are bad cops too, you know. I wouldn't trust a guy who asks a girl out while on duty."
msgstr "También hay policías malos. Yo no confiaría en un tipo que invita a salir a una chica mientras está de servicio."

msgctxt "8460_Maya"
msgid "You're right, but I'm a big girl. I can take care of myself."
msgstr "Tienes razón, pero soy una chica grande. Soy capaz de cuidarme sola."

msgctxt "8472_Maya"
msgid "You're not my father. You don't have protect me, okay?"
msgstr "No eres mi papá. No tienes que protegerme, ¿de acuerdo?"

msgctxt "8484_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "8496_Kiryu"
msgid "Sounds like the cops know your face now."
msgstr "Ahora parece que los policías te conocen."

msgctxt "8508_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, I guess so."
msgstr "Supongo que sí."

msgctxt "8520_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe you won't be stopped that much anymore."
msgstr "Quizá ya no te paren tanto."

msgctxt "8532_Maya"
msgid "Hmph. I'd rather be questioned by the cops than hit on."
msgstr "Mmm. Prefiero que la policía me interrogue a que me coqueteen."

msgctxt "8544_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, I can understand that."
msgstr "Sí, lo puedo entender."

msgctxt "8556_Maya"
msgid "But he's the only one who's tried to pick me up. The other ones still just question me."
msgstr "Pero es el único que ha intentado ligar conmigo. Los demás siguen limitándose a interrogarme."

msgctxt "8568_Kiryu"
msgid "Hmm. You sure you're not a wanted woman?"
msgstr "Mmm, ¿estás segura de que no eres una fugitiva?"

msgctxt "8580_Maya"
msgid "Who knows? Maybe I've got a price on my head!"
msgstr "¿Quién sabe? ¡Tal vez mi cabeza tiene un precio!"

msgctxt "8592_Maya"
msgid "I really don't understand why they question me so often, though."
msgstr "Sin embargo, no entiendo por qué me interrogan tan a menudo."

msgctxt "8604_Kiryu"
msgid "So, you were talking about quitting the club a while ago. Did you decide what to do?"
msgstr "Así que, ¿hablabas sobre abandonar el club hace tiempo? ¿Decidiste qué hacer?"

msgctxt "8616_Maya"
msgid "Well, I was planning on quitting, but..."
msgstr "Bueno, planeaba en renunciar, pero..."

msgctxt "8628_Kiryu"
msgid "You're not sure?"
msgstr "¿No estás segura?"

msgctxt "8640_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. Maybe I've had a change of heart."
msgstr "Sí. Tal vez tuve una corazonada."

msgctxt "8652_Maya"
msgid "What do you think? Should I quit?"
msgstr "¿Qué crees que deba hacer? ¿Debo renunciar?"

msgctxt "8664_Kiryu"
msgid "You don't want to quit, do you?"
msgstr "No quieres renunciar, ¿cierto?"

msgctxt "8676_Maya"
msgid "Huh? How did you know?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Cómo lo sabías?"

msgctxt "8688_Kiryu"
msgid "You just don't want to leave me, right? It's okay. You can say it."
msgstr "No quieres marcharte, ¿verdad? No pasa nada. Puedes decirlo."

msgctxt "8700_Maya"
msgid "Huh. That's pretty arrogant of you."
msgstr "Huh. Eso es bastante arrogante de tu parte."

msgctxt "8712_Maya"
msgid "It's as though you don't really care whether or not I stay."
msgstr "Es como si no te importara si me quedo o no."

msgctxt "8724_Maya"
msgid "You really don't understand women, do you?"
msgstr "Realmente no entiendes a las mujeres, ¿no?"

msgctxt "8736_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "8748_Kiryu"
msgid "You should follow your heart."
msgstr "Solo sigue a tu corazón."

msgctxt "8760_Maya"
msgid "But I don't know what I want to do. That's the problem."
msgstr "Pero no sé lo que quiero hacer. Esa es la cuestión."

msgctxt "8772_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, right. Well, you're still here. Doesn't that mean you don't want to quit?"
msgstr "Ah, cierto. Bueno, todavía estás aquí. ¿No significa eso que no quieres renunciar?"

msgctxt "8784_Maya"
msgid "I guess. But you keep talking about what I feel."
msgstr "Supongo. Pero sigues hablando de lo que siento."

msgctxt "8796_Maya"
msgid "I want to know what you think of me leaving."
msgstr "Quiero saber qué opinas que me vaya."

msgctxt "8808_Kiryu"
msgid "I already said. You should do what you want to do."
msgstr "Ya lo he dicho. Debes hacer lo que desees."

msgctxt "8820_Maya"
msgid "Oh. You can be kind of dense sometimes."
msgstr "Oh. Puedes ser un poco lento a veces."

msgctxt "8832_Kiryu"
msgid "You can't quit. You should keep working here."
msgstr "No puedes renunciar. Deberías seguir trabajando aquí."

msgctxt "8844_Maya"
msgid "Why?"
msgstr "¿Tú?"

msgctxt "8856_Kiryu"
msgid "Well... I like coming here and drinking with you."
msgstr "Porque... Me encanta estar contigo, charlando y bebiendo."

msgctxt "8868_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. Are you saying you'd miss me? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ji, ji. O sea, ¿qué me extrañarías? <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8880_Kiryu"
msgid "That's not really what I meant. It's just that as a customer, I'd prefer－"
msgstr "No es lo que quise decir. Es solo como cliente, prefiero -"

msgctxt "8892_Maya"
msgid "All right, all right. We can leave it at that. But I'll get you to say it someday."
msgstr "Está bien, está bien. Lo dejaremos así. Pero algún día lograré que lo digas."

msgctxt "8904_Kiryu"
msgid "You're quite a handful."
msgstr "Eres bastante difícil de tratar."

msgctxt "8916_Maya"
msgid "Do you ever go to other hostess clubs?"
msgstr "Do you ever go to other hostess clubs?"

msgctxt "8928_Kiryu"
msgid "Hmm? Well, I might go to other places from time to time.\\r\n"\n"I'm not always in Kamurocho, you know."
msgstr "Hmm? Well, I might go to other places from time to time.\\r\n"\n"I'm not always in Kamurocho, you know."

msgctxt "8940_Maya"
msgid "So you must have other girls you like drinking with, huh?"
msgstr "So you must have other girls you like drinking with, huh?"

msgctxt "8952_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. What's with the third degree all of a sudden? Are you feeling jealous?"
msgstr "Heh. What's with the third degree all of a sudden? Are you feeling jealous?"

msgctxt "8964_Maya"
msgid "Not jealous exactly. I just can't stand men who cheat."
msgstr "Not jealous exactly. I just can't stand men who cheat."

msgctxt "8976_Kiryu"
msgid "What counts as cheating? Is going to another hostess club cheating?"
msgstr "What counts as cheating? Is going to another hostess club cheating?"

msgctxt "8988_Maya"
msgid "It might if you were my boyfriend. But right now, I'd say requesting another hostess would be like cheating."
msgstr "It might if you were my boyfriend. But right now, I'd say requesting another hostess would be like cheating."

msgctxt "9000_Kiryu"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr "¿De verdad?"

msgctxt "9012_Maya"
msgid "Yes. So? Have you done that?"
msgstr "Yes. So? Have you done that?"

msgctxt "9024_Kiryu"
msgid "Me? I never request anybody at other clubs. I just stop by when I want a drink."
msgstr "Me? I never request anybody at other clubs. I just stop by when I want a drink."

msgctxt "9036_Maya"
msgid "Oh, okay. That makes me feel a little better. So I'm the only girl you request?"
msgstr "Oh, okay. That makes me feel a little better. So I'm the only girl you request?"

msgctxt "9048_Kiryu"
msgid "Uh, sure."
msgstr "Sí, claro."

msgctxt "9060_Kiryu"
msgid "Now you're just being silly. We're not dating. It's not your place to say what a customer can or can't do outside the club."
msgstr "Now you're just being silly. We're not dating. It's not your place to say what a customer can or can't do outside the club."

msgctxt "9072_Maya"
msgid "That must mean you've cheated on me.\\r\n"\n"That's horrible."
msgstr "That must mean you've cheated on me.\\r\n"\n"That's horrible."

msgctxt "9084_Kiryu"
msgid "Look, you're the one I have the most fun with. And you're the one I see the most often."
msgstr "Look, you're the one I have the most fun with. And you're the one I see the most often."

msgctxt "9096_Maya"
msgid "You probably tell that to the other girls, too."
msgstr "You probably tell that to the other girls, too."

msgctxt "9108_Kiryu"
msgid "No. Just you."
msgstr "No. Just you."

msgctxt "9120_Maya"
msgid "Hmph. You said that way too easily."
msgstr "Hmph. You said that way too easily."

msgctxt "9132_Maya"
msgid "I really thought you were different..."
msgstr "I really thought you were different..."

msgctxt "9144_Kiryu"
msgid "Do I look like the kind of man who'd cheat?"
msgstr "Do I look like the kind of man who'd cheat?"

msgctxt "9156_Maya"
msgid "No, you don't. You're a man who'd love someone for the rest of his life, once he gives his heart to them. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "No, you don't. You're a man who'd love someone for the rest of his life, once he gives his heart to them. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "9168_Kiryu"
msgid "Ever since I met you, there's been no one else."
msgstr "Ever since I met you, there's been no one else."

msgctxt "9180_Maya"
msgid "Really? That makes me so happy! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Really? That makes me so happy! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "9192_Kiryu"
msgid "And it's nice to know you're such a faithful woman, too."
msgstr "And it's nice to know you're such a faithful woman, too."

msgctxt "9204_Maya"
msgid "Yeah! If we started going out, we'd be in love until the day we die."
msgstr "Yeah! If we started going out, we'd be in love until the day we die."

msgctxt "9216_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Right."
msgstr "Heh. Right."

msgctxt "9228_Maya"
msgid "Do you come right out and tell a woman if you like her?"
msgstr "Do you come right out and tell a woman if you like her?"

msgctxt "9240_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh? Why do you ask?"
msgstr "Huh? Why do you ask?"

msgctxt "9252_Maya"
msgid "Just answer me."
msgstr "Just answer me."

msgctxt "9264_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, I'd tell her. I don't like to leave things up in the air."
msgstr "Yeah, I'd tell her. I don't like to leave things up in the air."

msgctxt "9276_Maya"
msgid "I knew it!"
msgstr "¡Lo sabía!"

msgctxt "9288_Kiryu"
msgid "What about you?"
msgstr "¿Qué hay de ti?"

msgctxt "9300_Maya"
msgid "I like the man to be the one to say it first."
msgstr "I like the man to be the one to say it first."

msgctxt "9312_Maya"
msgid "Then I'll say, \"Yes! I was waiting for you to say that!\""
msgstr "Then I'll say, \"Yes! I was waiting for you to say that!\""

msgctxt "9324_Kiryu"
msgid "What if you don't like the guy? It's not possible to like every man who falls for you, right?"
msgstr "What if you don't like the guy? It's not possible to like every man who falls for you, right?"

msgctxt "9336_Maya"
msgid "If I don't like him, I tell him that I'm not interested."
msgstr "If I don't like him, I tell him that I'm not interested."

msgctxt "9348_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh. If you're going to be picky and choose like that, why don't you just tell the guys you like first?"
msgstr "Huh. If you're going to be picky and choose like that, why don't you just tell the guys you like first?"

msgctxt "9360_Maya"
msgid "That's no good. The man has to take the initiative."
msgstr "That's no good. The man has to take the initiative."

msgctxt "9372_Maya"
msgid "So I'll be waiting if you have anything you want to tell me."
msgstr "So I'll be waiting if you have anything you want to tell me."

msgctxt "9384_Kiryu"
msgid "What's that supposed to mean?"
msgstr "¿Qué se supone que significa eso?"

msgctxt "9396_Kiryu"
msgid "You can't just sit back and wait for it. If you do, you might lose your chance."
msgstr "You can't just sit back and wait for it. If you do, you might lose your chance."

msgctxt "9408_Maya"
msgid "I dunno. There's just something wrong about the girl being the one to say it."
msgstr "I dunno. There's just something wrong about the girl being the one to say it."

msgctxt "9420_Kiryu"
msgid "But what if the guy is waiting for you to say something, too? You'll both wait forever."
msgstr "But what if the guy is waiting for you to say something, too? You'll both wait forever."

msgctxt "9432_Maya"
msgid "Well then, I would figure something out. I'll create a mood that'll make him confess his love for me."
msgstr "Well then, I would figure something out. I'll create a mood that'll make him confess his love for me."

msgctxt "9444_Kiryu"
msgid "That's practically the same thing as telling him, isn't it?"
msgstr "That's practically the same thing as telling him, isn't it?"

msgctxt "9456_Maya"
msgid "Why do you care!? You'd tell a girl if you like her, so what difference does it make!?"
msgstr "Why do you care!? You'd tell a girl if you like her, so what difference does it make!?"

msgctxt "9468_Kiryu"
msgid "Sorry."
msgstr "Lo siento."

msgctxt "9480_Kiryu"
msgid "Haven't you ever told someone yourself?"
msgstr "Haven't you ever told someone yourself?"

msgctxt "9492_Maya"
msgid "No comment!"
msgstr "No comment!"

msgctxt "9504_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. You're not afraid of being rejected, are you?"
msgstr "Heh. You're not afraid of being rejected, are you?"

msgctxt "9516_Maya"
msgid "No, I just think that the man should be the one to confess his love to the woman."
msgstr "No, I just think that the man should be the one to confess his love to the woman."

msgctxt "9528_Kiryu"
msgid "So women should be more passive?"
msgstr "So women should be more passive?"

msgctxt "9540_Maya"
msgid "Sure. Who wants an aggressive man-eater for a girlfriend?"
msgstr "Sure. Who wants an aggressive man-eater for a girlfriend?"

msgctxt "9552_Kiryu"
msgid "Good point..."
msgstr "Good point..."

msgctxt "9564_Maya"
msgid "Hmm!"
msgstr "Hmm!"

msgctxt "9576_Kiryu"
msgid "Did something good happen?"
msgstr "Did something good happen?"

msgctxt "9588_Maya"
msgid "Why do you ask?"
msgstr "Why do you ask?"

msgctxt "9600_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, you just seemed happy."
msgstr "Oh, you just seemed happy."

msgctxt "9612_Maya"
msgid "You think so, too?"
msgstr "You think so, too?"

msgctxt "9624_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Uh, ¿y eso?"

msgctxt "9636_Maya"
msgid "My friends always tell me I look happy, even when I'm not."
msgstr "My friends always tell me I look happy, even when I'm not."

msgctxt "9648_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, okay."
msgstr "Ah, entiendo."

msgctxt "9660_Maya"
msgid "I wonder why..."
msgstr "I wonder why..."

msgctxt "9672_Kiryu"
msgid "You look like you don't have any worries. If you act bright and cheery, of course people will think you're happy."
msgstr "You look like you don't have any worries. If you act bright and cheery, of course people will think you're happy."

msgctxt "9684_Maya"
msgid "Hey, that makes me sound like an airhead. I'm not cheerful all the time."
msgstr "Hey, that makes me sound like an airhead. I'm not cheerful all the time."

msgctxt "9696_Kiryu"
msgid " But I've never seen you upset. Do you try to keep your negative feelings from showing?"
msgstr " But I've never seen you upset. Do you try to keep your negative feelings from showing?"

msgctxt "9708_Maya"
msgid "I guess so. How you feel inside can affect how you look outside."
msgstr "I guess so. How you feel inside can affect how you look outside."

msgctxt "9720_Maya"
msgid "I always try to get rid of stress instead of bottling it up."
msgstr "I always try to get rid of stress instead of bottling it up."

msgctxt "9732_Kiryu"
msgid "So that's your beauty secret, huh?"
msgstr "So that's your beauty secret, huh?"

msgctxt "9744_Kiryu"
msgid "It's annoying when people jump to conclusions."
msgstr "It's annoying when people jump to conclusions."

msgctxt "9756_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. One of my friends is always being told that she doesn't look like she has a boyfriend."
msgstr "Yeah. One of my friends is always being told that she doesn't look like she has a boyfriend."

msgctxt "9768_Maya"
msgid "I don't think her feelings are really hurt by it, but it is irritating."
msgstr "I don't think her feelings are really hurt by it, but it is irritating."

msgctxt "9780_Kiryu"
msgid "You shouldn't judge people on their appearances."
msgstr "You shouldn't judge people on their appearances."

msgctxt "9792_Maya"
msgid "Right! I wish people would think before they say things like that. They probably wouldn't like it if they were on the receiving end."
msgstr "Right! I wish people would think before they say things like that. They probably wouldn't like it if they were on the receiving end."

msgctxt "9804_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "9816_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you have a hard time hiding your feelings?"
msgstr "Do you have a hard time hiding your feelings?"

msgctxt "9828_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. I can never get away with trying to hide something."
msgstr "Yeah. I can never get away with trying to hide something."

msgctxt "9840_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. I thought so."
msgstr "Heh. I thought so."

msgctxt "9852_Maya"
msgid "But people tell me I look happy, even when I'm not feeling very good."
msgstr "But people tell me I look happy, even when I'm not feeling very good."

msgctxt "9864_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh. I guess this is a different problem, then."
msgstr "Oh. I guess this is a different problem, then."

msgctxt "9876_Maya"
msgid "Nobody understands me. I've got problems like everybody else. I'm not happy all the time."
msgstr "Nobody understands me. I've got problems like everybody else. I'm not happy all the time."

msgctxt "9888_Kiryu"
msgid "What do you do to relax?"
msgstr "What do you do to relax?"

msgctxt "9900_Maya"
msgid "I go shopping, or I'm out drinking with my friends. Normal stuff, I guess."
msgstr "I go shopping, or I'm out drinking with my friends. Normal stuff, I guess."

msgctxt "9912_Kiryu"
msgid "Hmm. I'm a little surprised."
msgstr "Hmm. I'm a little surprised."

msgctxt "9924_Maya"
msgid "I used to go out to clubs all the time, but I had to cut back."
msgstr "I used to go out to clubs all the time, but I had to cut back."

msgctxt "9936_Maya"
msgid "You should've seen me when I was in high school."
msgstr "You should've seen me when I was in high school."

msgctxt "9948_Kiryu"
msgid "Everybody's a little wild at that age."
msgstr "Everybody's a little wild at that age."

msgctxt "9960_Maya"
msgid "All I cared about was looking good and having fun."
msgstr "All I cared about was looking good and having fun."

msgctxt "9972_Maya"
msgid "But around the time I turned twenty, my way of thinking changed. I started caring more about the kind of person I was on the inside."
msgstr "But around the time I turned twenty, my way of thinking changed. I started caring more about the kind of person I was on the inside."

msgctxt "9984_Maya"
msgid "So I don't go out and party like I used to anymore."
msgstr "So I don't go out and party like I used to anymore."

msgctxt "9996_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe you were too wild as a teenager. Besides, everyone's got to cut back on luxuries in this economy."
msgstr "Maybe you were too wild as a teenager. Besides, everyone's got to cut back on luxuries in this economy."

msgctxt "10008_Maya"
msgid "It does seem like people aren't spending as much on going out as they used to."
msgstr "It does seem like people aren't spending as much on going out as they used to."

msgctxt "10020_Kiryu"
msgid "It's good that you're happier this way."
msgstr "It's good that you're happier this way."

msgctxt "10032_Maya"
msgid "I really am. I've grown up a little bit, huh?"
msgstr "I really am. I've grown up a little bit, huh?"

msgctxt "10044_Maya"
msgid "Maybe someday I can become a woman others look up to."
msgstr "Maybe someday I can become a woman others look up to."

msgctxt "10056_Kiryu"
msgid "I think so."
msgstr "I think so."

msgctxt "10068_Kiryu"
msgid "I bet you hang out with a different crowd, too. When you're around adults, you realize how immature you are."
msgstr "I bet you hang out with a different crowd, too. When you're around adults, you realize how immature you are."

msgctxt "10080_Maya"
msgid "That's true! When I saw my friends growing up, I panicked a little bit."
msgstr "That's true! When I saw my friends growing up, I panicked a little bit."

msgctxt "10092_Maya"
msgid "So I decided to become a mature adult."
msgstr "So I decided to become a mature adult."

msgctxt "10104_Kiryu"
msgid "You'll have to work on your drinking, then."
msgstr "You'll have to work on your drinking, then."

msgctxt "10116_Maya"
msgid "I'm done with that! I haven't gotten drunk since last year!"
msgstr "I'm done with that! I haven't gotten drunk since last year!"

msgctxt "10128_Maya"
msgid "I take my time and enjoy what I drink."
msgstr "I take my time and enjoy what I drink."

msgctxt "10140_Kiryu"
msgid "That's good."
msgstr "Genial."

msgctxt "10152_Kiryu"
msgid "That's a surprisingly sensible thing to say. I'm impressed."
msgstr "That's a surprisingly sensible thing to say. I'm impressed."

msgctxt "10164_Maya"
msgid "What do you mean, surprisingly?"
msgstr "What do you mean, surprisingly?"

msgctxt "10176_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, you just don't look like you worry about that kind of thing. You're always smiling."
msgstr "Oh, you just don't look like you worry about that kind of thing. You're always smiling."

msgctxt "10188_Maya"
msgid "Well, you can't be a teenager forever. Sooner or later, you have to start acting your age."
msgstr "Well, you can't be a teenager forever. Sooner or later, you have to start acting your age."

msgctxt "10200_Maya"
msgid "But it works both ways. If you're not careful, you could get stuck in the past."
msgstr "But it works both ways. If you're not careful, you could get stuck in the past."

msgctxt "10212_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh. Yeah."
msgstr "Oh. Yeah."

msgctxt "10224_Maya"
msgid "What did you think the first time you saw me?"
msgstr "What did you think the first time you saw me?"

msgctxt "10236_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh? Why?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Por qué?"

msgctxt "10248_Maya"
msgid "A lot of people think I'm scary the first time they meet me."
msgstr "A lot of people think I'm scary the first time they meet me."

msgctxt "10260_Kiryu"
msgid "They do? That's a surprise."
msgstr "They do? That's a surprise."

msgctxt "10272_Maya"
msgid "I think it's because I'm a little shy at first. So I tense up and don't smile much."
msgstr "I think it's because I'm a little shy at first. So I tense up and don't smile much."

msgctxt "10284_Kiryu"
msgid "People say I'm scary, too. I know how you feel."
msgstr "People say I'm scary, too. I know how you feel."

msgctxt "10296_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, I thought so."
msgstr "Yeah, I thought so."

msgctxt "10308_Kiryu"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr "Oye."

msgctxt "10320_Maya"
msgid "But how can I stop people from thinking that?"
msgstr "But how can I stop people from thinking that?"

msgctxt "10332_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe it'd help if you made an effort to talk to them."
msgstr "Maybe it'd help if you made an effort to talk to them."

msgctxt "10344_Maya"
msgid "But that's the problem. I'm shy! I can't just jump in and talk to them."
msgstr "But that's the problem. I'm shy! I can't just jump in and talk to them."

msgctxt "10356_Kiryu"
msgid "You have to do your best. You might be embarrassed sometimes, but you'll get used to it eventually."
msgstr "You have to do your best. You might be embarrassed sometimes, but you'll get used to it eventually."

msgctxt "10368_Maya"
msgid "Okay. I'll give it a try next time."
msgstr "Okay. I'll give it a try next time."

msgctxt "10380_Maya"
msgid "Of course, I've never had any trouble smiling and talking to you."
msgstr "Of course, I've never had any trouble smiling and talking to you."

msgctxt "10392_Kiryu"
msgid "That's comforting."
msgstr "That's comforting."

msgctxt "10404_Kiryu"
msgid "That impression doesn't last long, does it? They probably don't think you're scary once they get to know you."
msgstr "That impression doesn't last long, does it? They probably don't think you're scary once they get to know you."

msgctxt "10416_Maya"
msgid "That's true. But what about people who've only met me once?"
msgstr "That's true. But what about people who've only met me once?"

msgctxt "10428_Maya"
msgid "If I hadn't scared them off, we might have become good friends."
msgstr "If I hadn't scared them off, we might have become good friends."

msgctxt "10440_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah... Still, you can't force yourself to act in a way that makes people like you. That would be tiring."
msgstr "Yeah... Still, you can't force yourself to act in a way that makes people like you. That would be tiring."

msgctxt "10452_Kiryu"
msgid "It's best to be yourself."
msgstr "It's best to be yourself."

msgctxt "10464_Maya"
msgid "Thank you. I feel a little better now."
msgstr "Thank you. I feel a little better now."

msgctxt "10476_Kiryu"
msgid "You've got a kind of aura about you. I could tell right away that you're something special."
msgstr "You've got a kind of aura about you. I could tell right away that you're something special."

msgctxt "10488_Maya"
msgid "Huh? What do you mean!?"
msgstr "Huh? What do you mean!?"

msgctxt "10500_Kiryu"
msgid "People are just intimidated. That's probably why they avoid you."
msgstr "People are just intimidated. That's probably why they avoid you."

msgctxt "10512_Maya"
msgid "Oh. That's kind of depressing."
msgstr "Oh. That's kind of depressing."

msgctxt "10524_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, it's better than everybody thinking they're your best friend, isn't it?"
msgstr "Well, it's better than everybody thinking they're your best friend, isn't it?"

msgctxt "10536_Maya"
msgid "No, it's not better at all! I don't want people to avoid me! That's terrible!"
msgstr "No, it's not better at all! I don't want people to avoid me! That's terrible!"

msgctxt "10548_Maya"
msgid "Ugh. What should I do?"
msgstr "Ugh. ¿Qué debería hacer?"

msgctxt "10560_Kiryu"
msgid "You haven't been drinking much. Are you feeling all right?"
msgstr "You haven't been drinking much. Are you feeling all right?"

msgctxt "10572_Maya"
msgid "I'm fine. I didn't want to get drunk and cause any trouble. I'm trying to cut back."
msgstr "I'm fine. I didn't want to get drunk and cause any trouble. I'm trying to cut back."

msgctxt "10584_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. You can be a little unpredictable when you're drunk."
msgstr "Heh. You can be a little unpredictable when you're drunk."

msgctxt "10596_Maya"
msgid "You got that right!"
msgstr "You got that right!"

msgctxt "10608_Maya"
msgid "This one time back in Yokohama, I did something really crazy."
msgstr "This one time back in Yokohama, I did something really crazy."

msgctxt "10620_Kiryu"
msgid "What was it?"
msgstr "¿Qué era?"

msgctxt "10632_Maya"
msgid "Well, apparently I ran around Chinatown with a corset wrapped around my waist."
msgstr "Well, apparently I ran around Chinatown with a corset wrapped around my waist."

msgctxt "10644_Kiryu"
msgid "A corset?"
msgstr "A corset?"

msgctxt "10656_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. You know, one of those medical corsets. My friend was wearing it for an injury."
msgstr "Yeah. You know, one of those medical corsets. My friend was wearing it for an injury."

msgctxt "10668_Kiryu"
msgid "And you put it on? Why would your friend be okay with that?"
msgstr "And you put it on? Why would your friend be okay with that?"

msgctxt "10680_Maya"
msgid "Um. I'm not sure she was..."
msgstr "Um. I'm not sure she was..."

msgctxt "10692_Kiryu"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

msgctxt "10704_Maya"
msgid "Hehe! She did say it took two extra weeks to heal because of me."
msgstr "Hehe! She did say it took two extra weeks to heal because of me."

msgctxt "10716_Kiryu"
msgid "Um... I think you should definitely cut back."
msgstr "Um... I think you should definitely cut back."

msgctxt "10728_Maya"
msgid "Me too."
msgstr "Yo también."

msgctxt "10740_Kiryu"
msgid "Apparently? You don't remember it?"
msgstr "Apparently? You don't remember it?"

msgctxt "10752_Maya"
msgid "Not at all! You'd think I would, but nope!"
msgstr "Not at all! You'd think I would, but nope!"

msgctxt "10764_Maya"
msgid "My friends said I made about three laps around Chinatown, screaming at the top of my lungs."
msgstr "My friends said I made about three laps around Chinatown, screaming at the top of my lungs."

msgctxt "10776_Kiryu"
msgid "That's really something."
msgstr "That's really something."

msgctxt "10788_Maya"
msgid "Oh, come on! Everybody's done something like that!"
msgstr "Oh, come on! Everybody's done something like that!"

msgctxt "10800_Kiryu"
msgid "Not that I can recall."
msgstr "Not that I can recall."

msgctxt "10812_Maya"
msgid "See! You were drinking so much you can't even remember it!"
msgstr "See! You were drinking so much you can't even remember it!"

msgctxt "10824_Kiryu"
msgid "That's not what I meant..."
msgstr "That's not what I meant..."

msgctxt "10836_Maya"
msgid "Oh, sure. We'll just leave it at that."
msgstr "Oh, sure. We'll just leave it at that."

msgctxt "10848_Kiryu"
msgid "Don't worry about it. Here, have a drink."
msgstr "Don't worry about it. Here, have a drink."

msgctxt "10860_Maya"
msgid "Wait, why should I?"
msgstr "Wait, why should I?"

msgctxt "10872_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, I'm interested to see what you'll do."
msgstr "Well, I'm interested to see what you'll do."

msgctxt "10884_Maya"
msgid "Hey, this isn't some kind of experiment!"
msgstr "Hey, this isn't some kind of experiment!"

msgctxt "10896_Maya"
msgid "And I have a reputation here. They know me as a calm, mature woman."
msgstr "And I have a reputation here. They know me as a calm, mature woman."

msgctxt "10908_Kiryu"
msgid "Uh-oh. I think you're already drunk. You're just talking nonsense now."
msgstr "Uh-oh. I think you're already drunk. You're just talking nonsense now."

msgctxt "10920_Maya"
msgid "What's that supposed to mean!?"
msgstr "¿¡Qué se supone que significa eso!?"

msgctxt "10932_Kiryu"
msgid "Haha."
msgstr "Ja, ja."

msgctxt "10944_Maya"
msgid "Do you enjoy talking with me?"
msgstr "Do you enjoy talking with me?"

msgctxt "10956_Kiryu"
msgid "Of course I do. Would I come back so many times if I didn't?"
msgstr "Of course I do. Would I come back so many times if I didn't?"

msgctxt "10968_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. ♪ Thanks. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Hehe. ♪ Thanks. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "10980_Kiryu"
msgid "What's wrong?"
msgstr "¿Qué ocurre?"

msgctxt "10992_Maya"
msgid "Well, I'm not very good at entertaining people."
msgstr "Well, I'm not very good at entertaining people."

msgctxt "11004_Maya"
msgid "I think I'm kind of boring compared to the other girls here. And I'm not well-educated, either."
msgstr "I think I'm kind of boring compared to the other girls here. And I'm not well-educated, either."

msgctxt "11016_Kiryu"
msgid "That's what I like about you. I love watching you try so hard to be entertaining."
msgstr "That's what I like about you. I love watching you try so hard to be entertaining."

msgctxt "11028_Maya"
msgid "Hey, are you making fun of me?"
msgstr "Hey, are you making fun of me?"

msgctxt "11040_Kiryu"
msgid "No, no. I'd rather have you try it your own way than copy what the other girls do."
msgstr "No, no. I'd rather have you try it your own way than copy what the other girls do."

msgctxt "11052_Maya"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr "¿De verdad?"

msgctxt "11064_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure. In fact, I want you to relax and be yourself instead of worrying about what I think."
msgstr "Sure. In fact, I want you to relax and be yourself instead of worrying about what I think."

msgctxt "11076_Maya"
msgid "Hmm..."
msgstr "Mmm..."

msgctxt "11088_Maya"
msgid "Okay! I'll try not to worry about it from now on!"
msgstr "Okay! I'll try not to worry about it from now on!"

msgctxt "11100_Kiryu"
msgid "Good."
msgstr "Perfecto."

msgctxt "11112_Kiryu"
msgid "Don't worry about that. You don't have to try so hard to be entertaining. Some people are better listeners than talkers."
msgstr "Don't worry about that. You don't have to try so hard to be entertaining. Some people are better listeners than talkers."

msgctxt "11124_Maya"
msgid "A better listener, huh? But I have trouble asking the right kind of follow-up questions."
msgstr "A better listener, huh? But I have trouble asking the right kind of follow-up questions."

msgctxt "11136_Kiryu"
msgid "Then the man should be talking about something more interesting."
msgstr "Then the man should be talking about something more interesting."

msgctxt "11148_Maya"
msgid "Haha! You're kinda strict toward men, aren't you?"
msgstr "Haha! You're kinda strict toward men, aren't you?"

msgctxt "11160_Kiryu"
msgid "Yes. A real gentleman should learn how to talk to a lady."
msgstr "Yes. A real gentleman should learn how to talk to a lady."

msgctxt "11172_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. You certainly know how to do that. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Hehe. You certainly know how to do that. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "11184_Kiryu"
msgid "Education isn't always a good thing. Some men prefer girls who aren't as well-educated as they are."
msgstr "Education isn't always a good thing. Some men prefer girls who aren't as well-educated as they are."

msgctxt "11196_Maya"
msgid "What about you?"
msgstr "¿Qué hay de ti?"

msgctxt "11208_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, I don't judge women like that, so it doesn't matter to me."
msgstr "Well, I don't judge women like that, so it doesn't matter to me."

msgctxt "11220_Maya"
msgid "Huh. That's not much help."
msgstr "Huh. That's not much help."

msgctxt "11232_Kiryu"
msgid "What your customers want is important, but so is knowing what kind of hostess you want to be."
msgstr "What your customers want is important, but so is knowing what kind of hostess you want to be."

msgctxt "11244_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. I know what my weaknesses are, so I can work to make them better."
msgstr "Yeah. I know what my weaknesses are, so I can work to make them better."

msgctxt "11256_Maya"
msgid "*yawns*"
msgstr "*yawns*"

msgctxt "11268_Kiryu"
msgid "You look tired. Did you have another photoshoot today?"
msgstr "You look tired. Did you have another photoshoot today?"

msgctxt "11280_Maya"
msgid "Oh, I'm sorry. Yes, I did. I had to get up really early today."
msgstr "Oh, I'm sorry. Yes, I did. I had to get up really early today."

msgctxt "11292_Maya"
msgid "If I'm not careful, I might fall asleep."
msgstr "If I'm not careful, I might fall asleep."

msgctxt "11304_Kiryu"
msgid "You could really sleep in a noisy place like this?"
msgstr "You could really sleep in a noisy place like this?"

msgctxt "11316_Maya"
msgid "Yep. Models are always a little sleep-deprived, so we catch a nap whenever we can."
msgstr "Yep. Models are always a little sleep-deprived, so we catch a nap whenever we can."

msgctxt "11328_Kiryu"
msgid "Aren't you working yourself a bit too hard? Maybe you should take some time off from the club."
msgstr "Aren't you working yourself a bit too hard? Maybe you should take some time off from the club."

msgctxt "11340_Maya"
msgid "But..."
msgstr "Pero..."

msgctxt "11352_Kiryu"
msgid "There's no point making money if you get sick. Your health is more important."
msgstr "There's no point making money if you get sick. Your health is more important."

msgctxt "11364_Maya"
msgid "I'm not here for the money. I'm here because I want to see you."
msgstr "I'm not here for the money. I'm here because I want to see you."

msgctxt "11376_Kiryu"
msgid "What? That's why...?"
msgstr "What? That's why...?"

msgctxt "11388_Maya"
msgid "But you thought I only cared about money! Maybe I should quit after all."
msgstr "But you thought I only cared about money! Maybe I should quit after all."

msgctxt "11400_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm sorry."
msgstr "Lo siento."

msgctxt "11412_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you fall asleep while doing your makeup?"
msgstr "Do you fall asleep while doing your makeup?"

msgctxt "11424_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, I've done that before. And some models even fall asleep while changing clothes."
msgstr "Yeah, I've done that before. And some models even fall asleep while changing clothes."

msgctxt "11436_Kiryu"
msgid "I thought models had to change clothes in a hurry so they could wear as many outfits as possible."
msgstr "I thought models had to change clothes in a hurry so they could wear as many outfits as possible."

msgctxt "11448_Maya"
msgid "That's just during fashion shows. It's more relaxed during shoots."
msgstr "That's just during fashion shows. It's more relaxed during shoots."

msgctxt "11460_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Sounds like fun."
msgstr "Je. Suena divertido."

msgctxt "11472_Maya"
msgid "It is. I hope I can be a model forever."
msgstr "It is. I hope I can be a model forever."

msgctxt "11484_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm a little disappointed. Modeling seems so glamorous, but in reality you get bags under your eyes."
msgstr "I'm a little disappointed. Modeling seems so glamorous, but in reality you get bags under your eyes."

msgctxt "11496_Maya"
msgid "Haha! That's okay. The makeup covers it up."
msgstr "Haha! That's okay. The makeup covers it up."

msgctxt "11508_Kiryu"
msgid "But you're not exactly relaxing and chatting in your dressing room."
msgstr "But you're not exactly relaxing and chatting in your dressing room."

msgctxt "11520_Maya"
msgid "Nope. You have to rest when you get the chance."
msgstr "Nope. You have to rest when you get the chance."

msgctxt "11532_Maya"
msgid "We try not to use any more energy than we have to."
msgstr "We try not to use any more energy than we have to."

msgctxt "11544_Kiryu"
msgid "Ah, I see."
msgstr "Oh, ya veo."

msgctxt "11556_Maya"
msgid "That policeman from before keeps emailing me. It's getting annoying."
msgstr "Ese policía de antes sigue enviándome correos. Me está volviendo loca."

msgctxt "11568_Kiryu"
msgid "You gave him your email address?"
msgstr "¿Le diste tu correo electrónico?"

msgctxt "11580_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. I thought knowing a policeman might come in handy."
msgstr "Sí. Pensé que conocer a un policía sería útil."

msgctxt "11592_Maya"
msgid "Now I'm regretting it."
msgstr "Y ahora me arrepiento..."

msgctxt "11604_Kiryu"
msgid "Let me know if it gets to be a problem. I've got a few connections in the Kamurocho Police."
msgstr "Avísame si llega a ser un problema. Tengo algunos contactos en la policía de Kamurocho."

msgctxt "11616_Maya"
msgid "You do? That might help."
msgstr "¿Lo harías? Eso podría ayudar."

msgctxt "11628_Kiryu"
msgid "But reporting a cop for stalking is a big deal, so..."
msgstr "Pero denunciar a un policía por acoso es un gran problema, así que..."

msgctxt "11640_Maya"
msgid "Haha, yeah. You're right. I'd like to see what would happen, though."
msgstr "Ja, ja. Tienes razón, pero me gustaría ver qué pasaría."

msgctxt "11652_Kiryu"
msgid "Let's just wait a bit longer and see if he gives up. If he doesn't stop after you ask him to, let me know."
msgstr "Esperemos un poco más a ver si se rinde. Si no para después de que se lo pidas, házmelo saber."

msgctxt "11664_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. Hopefully it won't come to that."
msgstr "Sí. Esperemos que no llegue a eso."

msgctxt "11676_Kiryu"
msgid "Why don't you just ignore his emails? That should take care of it."
msgstr "Why don't you just ignore his emails? That should take care of it."

msgctxt "11688_Maya"
msgid "I'm a little scared to do that."
msgstr "Me da un poco de miedo hacerlo."

msgctxt "11700_Kiryu"
msgid "Why?"
msgstr "¿Tú?"

msgctxt "11712_Maya"
msgid "He might make a big deal about me not responding to his messages."
msgstr "Puede que monte un escándalo porque no respondo a sus mensajes."

msgctxt "11724_Maya"
msgid "Instead of making him angry, I'd rather string him along with some boring messages until he gives up on his own."
msgstr "En lugar de enfadarle, prefiero darle largas con mensajes aburridos hasta que se rinda."

msgctxt "11736_Kiryu"
msgid "Okay. Well, this cop is still being a nuisance."
msgstr "De acuerdo. Bueno, este policía sigue siendo una molestia."

msgctxt "11748_Kiryu"
msgid "You shouldn't give your email to just anybody. Didn't you think this kind of thing might happen?"
msgstr "No deberías dar tu email a nadie. ¿No pensaste que este tipo de cosas podrían pasar?"

msgctxt "11760_Maya"
msgid "I know it was a mistake. I just didn't think it was a big deal."
msgstr "Sé que fue un error. Simplemente, no pensé que fuera para tanto."

msgctxt "11772_Kiryu"
msgid "You've got to be more careful. There are some bad people out there, you know."
msgstr "Tienes que tener más cuidado. Hay gente mala por ahí."

msgctxt "11784_Maya"
msgid "You don't have to rub it in. I figured he'd be safe, since he's a cop."
msgstr "No tienes que recordármelo. Pensé que estaría a salvo, ya que es policía."

msgctxt "11796_Maya"
msgid "I was hoping that you could give me a little advice, but I guess you're more interested in scolding me."
msgstr "Esperaba que pudieras aconsejarme, pero supongo que estás más interesado en regañarme."

msgctxt "11808_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "11820_Maya"
msgid "Do you think I should email him back? It can't be a good idea to ignore him, can it?"
msgstr "¿Crees que deba enviarle un email? No me parece correcto ignorarlo."

msgctxt "11832_Kiryu"
msgid "You're talking about that cop? What would you write?"
msgstr "¿Te refieres a ese policía? ¿Qué escribirías?"

msgctxt "11844_Maya"
msgid "I don't know. Do you have any ideas?"
msgstr "No lo sé... ¿Tienes alguna idea?"

msgctxt "11856_Kiryu"
msgid "Hmm. Well..."
msgstr "Mmm. Bueno..."

msgctxt "11868_Kiryu"
msgid "You could ask him to come to the club. You know, turn it into an advertisement."
msgstr "Puedes preguntarle si quiere que venga al club. Ya sabes, convertirlo en un anuncio."

msgctxt "11880_Maya"
msgid "What!? I don't want him showing up here!"
msgstr "¿¡Qué!? ¡No quiero que aparezca por aquí!"

msgctxt "11892_Kiryu"
msgid "But if you can't avoid him, at least this way you'll be getting paid for it."
msgstr "Pero si no puedes evitarlo, al menos te pagarán por invitarlo."

msgctxt "11904_Maya"
msgid "Well, yeah. But I don't want to see him at all."
msgstr "Bueno, sí. Pero no quiero verlo para nada."

msgctxt "11916_Maya"
msgid "If he did become one of my customers, I couldn't avoid him."
msgstr "Si se convirtiera en uno de mis clientes, no podría evitarlo."

msgctxt "11928_Kiryu"
msgid "Right. I guess that wasn't a very good idea."
msgstr "Cierto. Supongo que no fue una buena idea."

msgctxt "11940_Maya"
msgid "This is giving me such a headache."
msgstr "This is giving me such a headache."

msgctxt "11952_Kiryu"
msgid "You could say you've already got a boyfriend. That should make him give up."
msgstr "Podrías decir que ya tienes novio. Eso debería bastar para que se rinda."

msgctxt "11964_Maya"
msgid "I don't think so. He tries to pick up girls who are waiting for their dates. He wouldn't care."
msgstr "No lo creo. Intenta coquetear con chicas que están esperando a sus citas. No le importaría."

msgctxt "11976_Kiryu"
msgid "But if you at least say it, it wouldn't seem odd when you stop replying to his emails."
msgstr "Pero si lo dices, ya entenderá cuando dejes de responder a sus correos."

msgctxt "11988_Maya"
msgid "Oh, I hadn't thought of that."
msgstr "No lo había pensado..."

msgctxt "12000_Maya"
msgid "Okay, I'll try it. And you can be my boyfriend."
msgstr "Ok, lo intentaré. Y tú podrías ser mi novio."

msgctxt "12012_Maya"
msgid "That way, if he sees us together, I won't have to make up some excuse."
msgstr "Así, si nos ve juntos, no tendré que inventarme una excusa."

msgctxt "12024_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. Good."
msgstr "Je. Está bien."

msgctxt "12036_Kiryu"
msgid "You could ask him how much money he has. He might lose interest if he thinks that's all you care about."
msgstr "Podrías preguntarle cuánto dinero tiene. Podría perder interés si piensa que eso es lo único que te importa."

msgctxt "12048_Maya"
msgid "Hahaha! That could work!"
msgstr "Ja, ja, ja ¡Podría funcionar!"

msgctxt "12060_Maya"
msgid "But what if I ask him and he turns out to be super rich?"
msgstr "Pero, ¿y si se lo pido y resulta que es millonario?"

msgctxt "12072_Kiryu"
msgid "Come on. When's the last time you met a rich cop?\\r\n"\n"Especially one walking a beat."
msgstr "Vamos, ya. ¿Cuándo fue la última vez que conociste a un policía rico?\\r\n"\n"Especialmente uno que camina a ritmo."

msgctxt "12084_Maya"
msgid "You never know. Maybe his family's rich and he's doing police work for fun."
msgstr "Nunca se sabe. Tal vez su familia es rica y hace trabajo policial por diversión."

msgctxt "12096_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, it's possible."
msgstr "Bueno, es una posibilidad."

msgctxt "12108_Maya"
msgid "Hmm. I think I need another idea."
msgstr "Hmm. I think I need another idea."

msgctxt "12120_Maya"
msgid "I'm really thinking about quitting my job here."
msgstr "Realmente estoy pensando en renunciar aquí."

msgctxt "12132_Kiryu"
msgid "You are?"
msgstr "¿¡En serio!?"

msgctxt "12144_Maya"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "12156_Kiryu"
msgid "Okay... Do you mind telling me why?"
msgstr "Ok... ¿Y me puedes decir por qué?"

msgctxt "12168_Maya"
msgid "It was great when I started, since my boyfriend was working a night job, but now working here is getting in the way."
msgstr "Fue genial cuando empecé, ya que mi novio tenía un trabajo nocturno, pero ahora trabajar aquí me distrae."

msgctxt "12180_Kiryu"
msgid "In the way? Of what?"
msgstr "¿Te distrae? ¿De qué?"

msgctxt "12192_Maya"
msgid "Of... Of seeing you."
msgstr "De... De verte."

msgctxt "12204_Kiryu"
msgid "But you see me when I come to the club. Isn't that enough?"
msgstr "Pero, siempre me ves cuando vengo al club. ¿Eso no es suficiente?"

msgctxt "12216_Maya"
msgid "But then you're just one of my customers. I want our relationship to be more than that."
msgstr "Pero solo eres uno de mis clientes. Quiero que nuestra relación sea más que eso."

msgctxt "12228_Maya"
msgid "Unless you don't want it to be. Maybe I'm just a hostess to you."
msgstr "A menos que no quieras que lo sea. Tal vez solo soy una Hostess para ti."

msgctxt "12240_Kiryu"
msgid "That's not true. I don't want our relationship to end at the club."
msgstr "Eso no es cierto. No quiero que nuestra relación termine en el club."

msgctxt "12252_Maya"
msgid "Really!?"
msgstr "¡¿En serio?!"

msgctxt "12264_Kiryu"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "12276_Maya"
msgid "Yay! I'm so happy! ♪"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Estoy muy feliz! ♪"

msgctxt "12288_Maya"
msgid "But remember, I'll kill you if you request other hostesses after I quit."
msgstr "Pero recuerda, te mataré si solicitas otras Hostess después de que renuncie."

msgctxt "12300_Kiryu"
msgid "You don't have to worry about that. I think..."
msgstr "No tienes que preocuparte por eso. Creo..."

msgctxt "12312_Kiryu"
msgid "You'd quit your job for me?"
msgstr "¿Renunciarías por mí?"

msgctxt "12324_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. It's more for me than for you. I'm quitting because I want to see more of you."
msgstr "Je, je. Es más por mí que por ti. Lo dejo porque quiero ver más de ti."

msgctxt "12336_Kiryu"
msgid "I spend a lot of time out at night, you know."
msgstr "Paso mucho tiempo fuera por la noche."

msgctxt "12348_Maya"
msgid "Huh? You do?"
msgstr "¿De verdad?"

msgctxt "12360_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. Actually, I'm out almost all the time. I'm pretty busy. I don't have a lot of time to relax."
msgstr "Sí. En realidad, estoy fuera casi todo el tiempo. Estoy muy ocupado. No tengo mucho tiempo para relajarme."

msgctxt "12372_Maya"
msgid "But you have enough time to come here."
msgstr "Pero tienes tiempo de sobra para venir aquí."

msgctxt "12384_Kiryu"
msgid "I make time to. It helps me get rid of stress. If I didn't come, I'd probably get sick."
msgstr "Saco tiempo para hacerlo. Me ayuda a liberarme del estrés. Si no viniera, probablemente me pondría mal."

msgctxt "12396_Maya"
msgid "Hmm. It sounds like it would be better if I just stayed here."
msgstr "Mmm. Parece que sería mejor que me quedara aquí."

msgctxt "12408_Maya"
msgid "Aw. And I'd finally made up my mind, too."
msgstr "Aw. And I'd finally made up my mind, too."

msgctxt "12420_Kiryu"
msgid "I guess I hadn't mentioned this before, but I actually live in Okinawa."
msgstr "Cree que nunca te lo dije... Pero yo vivo en Okinawa."

msgctxt "12432_Maya"
msgid "What!? You do!?"
msgstr "¿¡Qué!?"

msgctxt "12444_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. I've been taking care of some business here, but I'll go home when things are settled."
msgstr "Sí. He estado ocupándome de algunos asuntos aquí, pero volveré a casa cuando las cosas estén arregladas."

msgctxt "12456_Maya"
msgid "Oh. I see."
msgstr "Oh, entiendo."

msgctxt "12468_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm sorry."
msgstr "Lo siento."

msgctxt "12480_Maya"
msgid "No! I don't mind!"
msgstr "¡No, no! ¡Me parece excelente!"

msgctxt "12492_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Uh, ¿y eso?"

msgctxt "12504_Maya"
msgid "I'll go with you to Okinawa!"
msgstr "I'll go with you to Okinawa!"

msgctxt "12516_Kiryu"
msgid "What!? You will?"
msgstr "What!? You will?"

msgctxt "12528_Maya"
msgid "Yes! A devoted woman like me won't let such a little thing get in the way. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Sí! Una mujer devota como yo no dejará que algo tan insignificante se interponga en su camino. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "12540_Kiryu"
msgid "Haha, I guess not."
msgstr "Ja, ja. Supongo que no."

msgctxt "12552_Maya"
msgid "Remember how I told you about my friend whose boyfriend cheated on her?"
msgstr "¿Recuerdas que te hablé de mi amiga cuyo novio la engañó?"

msgctxt "12564_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr "Claro."

msgctxt "12576_Maya"
msgid "Well, things kept on getting worse for her."
msgstr "Bueno, las cosas siguieron empeorando para ella."

msgctxt "12588_Kiryu"
msgid "That's too bad."
msgstr "Eso es... una pena."

msgctxt "12600_Maya"
msgid "I've been thinking of telling her to leave him. I'm not sure if it's my place to, though."
msgstr "He estado pensando en decirle que lo deje. Aunque no estoy segura de si me corresponde a mí hacerlo."

msgctxt "12612_Maya"
msgid "I just want her to be happy."
msgstr "Solo quiero que sea feliz."

msgctxt "12624_Kiryu"
msgid "Sounds like a good idea. I don't know her, but it isn't healthy to be in a relationship with a man who keeps on cheating."
msgstr "Parece una buena idea. No la conozco, pero no es sano estar en una relación con un hombre que la sigue engañando."

msgctxt "12636_Maya"
msgid "Right!"
msgstr "¡Tienes razón!"

msgctxt "12648_Maya"
msgid "Still, she's pretty serious about him. You'd think she'd leave him, but..."
msgstr "Aun así, ella va muy en serio con él. Uno pensaría que ella lo dejaría, pero..."

msgctxt "12660_Kiryu"
msgid "Wait, she's not thinking about marrying him, is she?"
msgstr "Wait, she's not thinking about marrying him, is she?"

msgctxt "12672_Maya"
msgid "Yes..."
msgstr "Sí..."

msgctxt "12684_Maya"
msgid "That's why I don't know if this is something I should be getting involved with."
msgstr "That's why I don't know if this is something I should be getting involved with."

msgctxt "12696_Kiryu"
msgid "But you could save her from a lifetime of unhappiness."
msgstr "But you could save her from a lifetime of unhappiness."

msgctxt "12708_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. Yeah, you're right! Thanks for listening!"
msgstr "Yeah. Yeah, you're right! Thanks for listening!"

msgctxt "12720_Kiryu"
msgid "I don't think you should get involved. You could end up making things worse."
msgstr "I don't think you should get involved. You could end up making things worse."

msgctxt "12732_Maya"
msgid "So I should just stay out of it?"
msgstr "So I should just stay out of it?"

msgctxt "12744_Kiryu"
msgid "No, not exactly. You should be there for her if she needs someone to talk to."
msgstr "No, not exactly. You should be there for her if she needs someone to talk to."

msgctxt "12756_Kiryu"
msgid "But just listen. Don't bring your own opinion into it."
msgstr "But just listen. Don't bring your own opinion into it."

msgctxt "12768_Maya"
msgid "But why can't I say anything?"
msgstr "But why can't I say anything?"

msgctxt "12780_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, when people are depressed, an off-hand comment can hurt. You might do more harm than good."
msgstr "Well, when people are depressed, an off-hand comment can hurt. You might do more harm than good."

msgctxt "12792_Kiryu"
msgid "It's better to let her heal over time."
msgstr "It's better to let her heal over time."

msgctxt "12804_Maya"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "Está bien."

msgctxt "12816_Maya"
msgid "I guess being a friend means knowing when to give someone space. Thanks for the advice. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I guess being a friend means knowing when to give someone space. Thanks for the advice. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "12828_Kiryu"
msgid "There are no right or wrong answers in love. Everybody's values are different."
msgstr "There are no right or wrong answers in love. Everybody's values are different."

msgctxt "12840_Kiryu"
msgid "Even if you do what you think is right, there's no guarantee that it'll be right for her."
msgstr "Even if you do what you think is right, there's no guarantee that it'll be right for her."

msgctxt "12852_Maya"
msgid "What? You mean you think they should stay together?"
msgstr "What? You mean you think they should stay together?"

msgctxt "12864_Kiryu"
msgid "Not necessarily. But it's not our place to decide what's best for them."
msgstr "Not necessarily. But it's not our place to decide what's best for them."

msgctxt "12876_Maya"
msgid "Then I can't do anything for her..."
msgstr "Then I can't do anything for her..."

msgctxt "12888_Kiryu"
msgid "It's better for her and for you if you don't get too involved."
msgstr "It's better for her and for you if you don't get too involved."

msgctxt "12900_Kiryu"
msgid "Just tell her what you honestly feel. Then she can decide what she wants to do."
msgstr "Just tell her what you honestly feel. Then she can decide what she wants to do."

msgctxt "12912_Kiryu"
msgid "Even if it ends your friendship, it's better than regretting that you never said anything."
msgstr "Even if it ends your friendship, it's better than regretting that you never said anything."

msgctxt "12924_Maya"
msgid "Oh... This is tough."
msgstr "Oh... This is tough."

msgctxt "12936_Maya"
msgid "Thank you. I'll do my best to make her understand how I feel."
msgstr "Thank you. I'll do my best to make her understand how I feel."

msgctxt "12948_Maya"
msgid "Do you think we'll always be like this?"
msgstr "Do you think we'll always be like this?"

msgctxt "12960_Kiryu"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿A qué te refieres?"

msgctxt "12972_Maya"
msgid "Always a hostess and a customer."
msgstr "Always a hostess and a customer."

msgctxt "12984_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "Oh."

msgctxt "12996_Maya"
msgid "I can't be a hostess for the rest of my life. This club won't be around forever."
msgstr "I can't be a hostess for the rest of my life. This club won't be around forever."

msgctxt "13008_Maya"
msgid "And you have to pay to come here and see me."
msgstr "And you have to pay to come here and see me."

msgctxt "13020_Maya"
msgid "This can't last forever, can it?"
msgstr "This can't last forever, can it?"

msgctxt "13032_Kiryu"
msgid "It'll be all right. This kind of thing can keep going for a long time."
msgstr "It'll be all right. This kind of thing can keep going for a long time."

msgctxt "13044_Maya"
msgid "That's all you want from our relationship?"
msgstr "That's all you want from our relationship?"

msgctxt "13056_Kiryu"
msgid "Is there a problem with that?"
msgstr "Is there a problem with that?"

msgctxt "13068_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. I need more. I've got hopes and dreams."
msgstr "Yeah. I need more. I've got hopes and dreams."

msgctxt "13080_Kiryu"
msgid "Like what?"
msgstr "Un sueño..."

msgctxt "13092_Maya"
msgid "Well, you know..."
msgstr "Well, you know..."

msgctxt "13104_Kiryu"
msgid "I know?"
msgstr "I know?"

msgctxt "13116_Maya"
msgid "Oh, come on! Can't you even figure that much out!?"
msgstr "Oh, come on! Can't you even figure that much out!?"

msgctxt "13128_Kiryu"
msgid "...?"
msgstr "...?"

msgctxt "13140_Kiryu"
msgid "That depends on us. We might not be able to stay hostess and customer, but we're more than that."
msgstr "That depends on us. We might not be able to stay hostess and customer, but we're more than that."

msgctxt "13152_Kiryu"
msgid "We can see each other outside of the club, can't we?"
msgstr "We can see each other outside of the club, can't we?"

msgctxt "13164_Maya"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr "¡Sí!"

msgctxt "13176_Maya"
msgid "But we'd be taking a step towards becoming a real couple..."
msgstr "But we'd be taking a step towards becoming a real couple..."

msgctxt "13188_Kiryu"
msgid "I suppose."
msgstr "I suppose."

msgctxt "13200_Maya"
msgid "I don't know. I'm not even sure what I really want yet."
msgstr "I don't know. I'm not even sure what I really want yet."

msgctxt "13212_Kiryu"
msgid "There's no reason to hurry, is there? We don't have to change right now."
msgstr "There's no reason to hurry, is there? We don't have to change right now."

msgctxt "13224_Maya"
msgid "You're right."
msgstr "Tienes razón."

msgctxt "13236_Maya"
msgid "Ugh! I just don't know what to do!"
msgstr "Ugh! I just don't know what to do!"

msgctxt "13248_Kiryu"
msgid "Hahaha!"
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja!"

msgctxt "13260_Kiryu"
msgid "It could be time for us to move on. Maybe I  shouldn't see you anymore."
msgstr "It could be time for us to move on. Maybe I  shouldn't see you anymore."

msgctxt "13272_Maya"
msgid "What!? No! That's not what I meant at all!"
msgstr "What!? No! That's not what I meant at all!"

msgctxt "13284_Maya"
msgid "This is terrible..."
msgstr "This is terrible..."

msgctxt "13296_Kiryu"
msgid "Just kidding. I'll keep coming to see you."
msgstr "Just kidding. I'll keep coming to see you."

msgctxt "13308_Maya"
msgid "Huh!? Hey! You shouldn't play with a girl's feelings like that!"
msgstr "Huh!? Hey! You shouldn't play with a girl's feelings like that!"

msgctxt "13320_Kiryu"
msgid "Er, sorry."
msgstr "Lo siento..."

msgctxt "13332_Maya"
msgid "Ugh. Now I'm having second thoughts about you in general."
msgstr "Ugh. Now I'm having second thoughts about you in general."

msgctxt "13344_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "13356_Maya"
msgid "I haven't been sleeping well lately."
msgstr "I haven't been sleeping well lately."

msgctxt "13368_Kiryu"
msgid "Are you okay?"
msgstr "¿Estás bien?"

msgctxt "13380_Maya"
msgid "I think so, but..."
msgstr "I think so, but..."

msgctxt "13392_Maya"
msgid "Hehe."
msgstr "Je, je."

msgctxt "13404_Kiryu"
msgid "Uh... What's so funny?"
msgstr "Uh... What's so funny?"

msgctxt "13416_Maya"
msgid "Oh, I was just remembering something from a long time ago."
msgstr "Oh, I was just remembering something from a long time ago."

msgctxt "13428_Maya"
msgid "One time in high school, I went to bed on Sunday night and woke up on Tuesday morning!"
msgstr "One time in high school, I went to bed on Sunday night and woke up on Tuesday morning!"

msgctxt "13440_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh!? What happened to Monday?"
msgstr "Huh!? What happened to Monday?"

msgctxt "13452_Kiryu"
msgid "You slept through an entire day?"
msgstr "You slept through an entire day?"

msgctxt "13464_Maya"
msgid "Hahaha! I didn't even notice until I got an email from a friend."
msgstr "Hahaha! I didn't even notice until I got an email from a friend."

msgctxt "13476_Maya"
msgid "She was like, \"Aren't you coming to school today?\" I had no idea what she was talking about."
msgstr "She was like, \"Aren't you coming to school today?\" I had no idea what she was talking about."

msgctxt "13488_Maya"
msgid "Then I noticed that the message was dated Monday morning! That's when I realized it was Tuesday!"
msgstr "Then I noticed that the message was dated Monday morning! That's when I realized it was Tuesday!"

msgctxt "13500_Kiryu"
msgid "How could something like that happen? Don't most people wake up after eight hours?"
msgstr "How could something like that happen? Don't most people wake up after eight hours?"

msgctxt "13512_Maya"
msgid "Well, before I went to bed, I had been partying all weekend."
msgstr "Well, before I went to bed, I had been partying all weekend."

msgctxt "13524_Kiryu"
msgid "Ah. I see."
msgstr "Ah. I see."

msgctxt "13536_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, I was pretty crazy back then."
msgstr "Yeah, I was pretty crazy back then."

msgctxt "13548_Kiryu"
msgid "Apparently. But you got a good story out of it."
msgstr "Apparently. But you got a good story out of it."

msgctxt "13560_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. I haven't thought about it in a long time."
msgstr "Hehe. I haven't thought about it in a long time."

msgctxt "13572_Kiryu"
msgid "Why didn't your family wake you up? You had school on Monday, right?"
msgstr "Why didn't your family wake you up? You had school on Monday, right?"

msgctxt "13584_Maya"
msgid "Well, sometimes I wouldn't come home for a day or two, so they probably didn't know I was asleep in my room."
msgstr "Well, sometimes I wouldn't come home for a day or two, so they probably didn't know I was asleep in my room."

msgctxt "13596_Kiryu"
msgid "What!? Your parents let you stay out for days?"
msgstr "What!? Your parents let you stay out for days?"

msgctxt "13608_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, but it's not their fault. I was quite a handful back then."
msgstr "Yeah, but it's not their fault. I was quite a handful back then."

msgctxt "13620_Kiryu"
msgid "But parents have a responsibility to look after their kids. You could've been hurt."
msgstr "But parents have a responsibility to look after their kids. You could've been hurt."

msgctxt "13632_Maya"
msgid "I understand, but don't think badly of my parents.\\r\n"\n"It really was my fault."
msgstr "I understand, but don't think badly of my parents.\\r\n"\n"It really was my fault."

msgctxt "13644_Kiryu"
msgid "Are you sure you weren't in a coma? You're lucky you woke up at all."
msgstr "Are you sure you weren't in a coma? You're lucky you woke up at all."

msgctxt "13656_Maya"
msgid "Heh, you might be right."
msgstr "Puede que tengas razón."

msgctxt "13668_Maya"
msgid "When I woke up I was really dehydrated, so I drank a whole bottle of water. Then I threw it up."
msgstr "When I woke up I was really dehydrated, so I drank a whole bottle of water. Then I threw it up."

msgctxt "13680_Kiryu"
msgid "Your body was in shock. You have to drink little by little at times like that."
msgstr "Your body was in shock. You have to drink little by little at times like that."

msgctxt "13692_Maya"
msgid "You know a lot about this kind of thing, huh?"
msgstr "You know a lot about this kind of thing, huh?"

msgctxt "13704_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah. I studied a bit so I'd know what to do in case something happened to one of the kids."
msgstr "Yeah. I studied a bit so I'd know what to do in case something happened to one of the kids."

msgctxt "13716_Maya"
msgid "Well then, you can wake me up the next time I sleep too long. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Well then, you can wake me up the next time I sleep too long. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "13728_Maya"
msgid "I've been thinking about doing yoga."
msgstr "I've been thinking about doing yoga."

msgctxt "13740_Kiryu"
msgid "Yoga?"
msgstr "Yoga?"

msgctxt "13752_Maya"
msgid "Yep. Have you ever done it?"
msgstr "Yep. Have you ever done it?"

msgctxt "13764_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm afraid not."
msgstr "I'm afraid not."

msgctxt "13776_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, you don't seem like the yoga type."
msgstr "Yeah, you don't seem like the yoga type."

msgctxt "13788_Kiryu"
msgid "What made you think about taking it up?"
msgstr "What made you think about taking it up?"

msgctxt "13800_Maya"
msgid "Well... My body is going to change as I get older. I figured I should start doing something about it."
msgstr "Well... My body is going to change as I get older. I figured I should start doing something about it."

msgctxt "13812_Kiryu"
msgid "You don't need to worry about that. You're so thin now. You'll be fine."
msgstr "You don't need to worry about that. You're so thin now. You'll be fine."

msgctxt "13824_Maya"
msgid "You'd be surprised how quickly a girl can go downhill."
msgstr "You'd be surprised how quickly a girl can go downhill."

msgctxt "13836_Kiryu"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr "¿De verdad?"

msgctxt "13848_Maya"
msgid "Sure. I see girls who are younger than me and notice how much nicer they look. They're so thin."
msgstr "Sure. I see girls who are younger than me and notice how much nicer they look. They're so thin."

msgctxt "13860_Kiryu"
msgid "That's silly. You're thinner and prettier than most girls. You don't have anything to worry about."
msgstr "That's silly. You're thinner and prettier than most girls. You don't have anything to worry about."

msgctxt "13872_Maya"
msgid "Hmph. Men just don't get it."
msgstr "Hmph. Men just don't get it."

msgctxt "13884_Kiryu"
msgid "Like how men do weight training?"
msgstr "Like how men do weight training?"

msgctxt "13896_Maya"
msgid "That's right! It's the same thing."
msgstr "That's right! It's the same thing."

msgctxt "13908_Maya"
msgid "Men who were fit when they were young end up with beer bellies if they aren't careful. It's sad."
msgstr "Men who were fit when they were young end up with beer bellies if they aren't careful. It's sad."

msgctxt "13920_Kiryu"
msgid "Staying fit isn't that hard, but getting back what you've lost is another story."
msgstr "Staying fit isn't that hard, but getting back what you've lost is another story."

msgctxt "13932_Maya"
msgid "Exactly. That's why I should start doing something now."
msgstr "Exactly. That's why I should start doing something now."

msgctxt "13944_Maya"
msgid "Oh, I know! You can do yoga with me! You'd get really flexible!"
msgstr "Oh, I know! You can do yoga with me! You'd get really flexible!"

msgctxt "13956_Kiryu"
msgid "Uh, I'll pass."
msgstr "Uh, I'll pass."

msgctxt "13968_Kiryu"
msgid "Actually, you could stand to gain some weight. You're already too thin."
msgstr "Actually, you could stand to gain some weight. You're already too thin."

msgctxt "13980_Maya"
msgid "What!? You're kidding me!"
msgstr "What!? You're kidding me!"

msgctxt "13992_Kiryu"
msgid "If you diet too much when you're young, it can become a serious problem when you're older."
msgstr "If you diet too much when you're young, it can become a serious problem when you're older."

msgctxt "14004_Maya"
msgid "But yoga should be fine, right? If anything, it will get me into better shape."
msgstr "But yoga should be fine, right? If anything, it will get me into better shape."

msgctxt "14016_Kiryu"
msgid " As long as you eat well, yes. But without a healthy lifestyle, you could end up hurting yourself."
msgstr " As long as you eat well, yes. But without a healthy lifestyle, you could end up hurting yourself."

msgctxt "14028_Maya"
msgid "Yeah. And working as a hostess makes it hard to get enough sleep."
msgstr "Yeah. And working as a hostess makes it hard to get enough sleep."

msgctxt "14040_Kiryu"
msgid "Then that's what you need to work on first."
msgstr "Then that's what you need to work on first."

msgctxt "14052_Maya"
msgid "Okay. Thanks for the advice!"
msgstr "Okay. Thanks for the advice!"

msgctxt "14064_Maya"
msgid "I haven't been going out recently, except for work."
msgstr "I haven't been going out recently, except for work."

msgctxt "14076_Kiryu"
msgid "What do you do at home?"
msgstr "What do you do at home?"

msgctxt "14088_Maya"
msgid "Mostly, I watch DVDs of foreign TV shows."
msgstr "Mostly, I watch DVDs of foreign TV shows."

msgctxt "14100_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh. I keep hearing people say that. I guess it's a popular hobby."
msgstr "Huh. I keep hearing people say that. I guess it's a popular hobby."

msgctxt "14112_Maya"
msgid "Well, I'm not doing it because it's popular. Remember how I was a wild kid?"
msgstr "Well, I'm not doing it because it's popular. Remember how I was a wild kid?"

msgctxt "14124_Maya"
msgid "Now I'm doing my best to act my age, so I just stay home."
msgstr "Now I'm doing my best to act my age, so I just stay home."

msgctxt "14136_Kiryu"
msgid "Is that such a good idea? You should try to do things outdoors, too."
msgstr "Is that such a good idea? You should try to do things outdoors, too."

msgctxt "14148_Maya"
msgid "I know. I like to travel. And I love to go to the beach and play water sports."
msgstr "I know. I like to travel. And I love to go to the beach and play water sports."

msgctxt "14160_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, you do have an active side, then. I'm a bit surprised."
msgstr "Oh, you do have an active side, then. I'm a bit surprised."

msgctxt "14172_Maya"
msgid "See? I figure it's okay for me to spend time indoors, too."
msgstr "See? I figure it's okay for me to spend time indoors, too."

msgctxt "14184_Kiryu"
msgid "Just try not to cause trouble for the neighbors."
msgstr "Just try not to cause trouble for the neighbors."

msgctxt "14196_Maya"
msgid "Hey, what do you think I do at home, anyway?"
msgstr "Hey, what do you think I do at home, anyway?"

msgctxt "14208_Maya"
msgid "A mature woman like me is always quiet and well-behaved."
msgstr "A mature woman like me is always quiet and well-behaved."

msgctxt "14220_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, sure..."
msgstr "Oh, sure..."

msgctxt "14232_Kiryu"
msgid "You're just shutting out the outside world. Is that something a mature woman would do?"
msgstr "You're just shutting out the outside world. Is that something a mature woman would do?"

msgctxt "14244_Maya"
msgid "What do you mean? Enjoying alone time at home at night proves that I'm an adult."
msgstr "What do you mean? Enjoying alone time at home at night proves that I'm an adult."

msgctxt "14256_Kiryu"
msgid "But aren't most people home at night?"
msgstr "But aren't most people home at night?"

msgctxt "14268_Maya"
msgid "Huh? Are they?"
msgstr "Huh? Are they?"

msgctxt "14280_Kiryu"
msgid "What do you mean, \"Are they?\" Don't tell me you spent literally every night partying as a kid?"
msgstr "What do you mean, \"Are they?\" Don't tell me you spent literally every night partying as a kid?"

msgctxt "14292_Maya"
msgid "Of course not. Sometimes I partied during the day, too!"
msgstr "Of course not. Sometimes I partied during the day, too!"

msgctxt "14304_Kiryu"
msgid "So you partied 24 hours a day...?"
msgstr "So you partied 24 hours a day...?"

msgctxt "14316_Kiryu"
msgid "You've really grown. Now you just need to learn how to cook and sew."
msgstr "You've really grown. Now you just need to learn how to cook and sew."

msgctxt "14328_Maya"
msgid "I know! I'm on my way to becoming the perfect woman."
msgstr "I know! I'm on my way to becoming the perfect woman."

msgctxt "14340_Kiryu"
msgid "But wait, you're just lying around watching DVDs, right? Is that a mature thing to do?"
msgstr "But wait, you're just lying around watching DVDs, right? Is that a mature thing to do?"

msgctxt "14352_Maya"
msgid "Oh, I can worry about the other stuff once I find a boyfriend."
msgstr "Oh, I can worry about the other stuff once I find a boyfriend."

msgctxt "14364_Kiryu"
msgid "What if you lose your figure? You might not be able to find a boyfriend then."
msgstr "What if you lose your figure? You might not be able to find a boyfriend then."

msgctxt "14376_Maya"
msgid "Oh no! I hadn't thought of that. I really should start doing yoga!"
msgstr "Oh no! I hadn't thought of that. I really should start doing yoga!"

msgctxt "14388_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh."
msgstr "Je."

msgctxt "14400_Maya"
