msgstr "That's right! I hate that stuff!"

msgctxt "14460_Maya"
msgid "When I see it on my noodles I wanna scream, \"Get lost, ginger! Who needs you!?\""
msgstr "When I see it on my noodles I wanna scream, \"Get lost, ginger! Who needs you!?\""

